Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:36.36,中文,,0,0,0,,我曾以为这就是你故事的起点\N{\r英文}I used to think this was the beginning of your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:45.68,中文,,0,0,0,,记忆这东西作风诡异\N{\r英文}Memory is a strange thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:49.68,中文,,0,0,0,,总是让我琢磨不透\N{\r英文}It doesn't work like I thought it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:52.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我们完全受制于时间\N{\r英文}We are so bound by time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:55.92,中文,,0,0,0,,要跟随它的节拍\N{\r英文}by its order.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:17.56,中文,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\r英文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:26.40,中文,,0,0,0,,好了，回到妈妈身边吧\N{\r英文}Okay, come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:28.13,中文,,0,0,0,,到妈妈怀里来\N{\r英文}Come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:31.08,中文,,0,0,0,,到妈妈怀里来\N{\r英文}Come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:32.57,中文,,0,0,0,,举起手来！\N{\r英文}Stick 'em up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:37.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你就是这镇上的警长吗？\N{\r英文}Are you the sheriff in this here town?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:40.73,中文,,0,0,0,,我拿着挠痒枪，现在要来收拾你了\N{\r英文}These are my tickle guns, and I'm gonna get ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:42.48,中文,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\r英文}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:45.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你想让我去抓你？那你快点逃吧\N{\r英文}You want me to chase you? You better run.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我记得故事中间的片段\N{\r英文}I remember moments in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:12.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\r英文}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:15.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我恨你！\N{\r英文}I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:29.01,中文,,0,0,0,,这就是终点了\N{\r英文}And this was the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:39.48,中文,,0,0,0,,回到妈妈身边\N{\r英文}Come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:41.76,中文,,0,0,0,,回到妈妈身边好吗\N{\r英文}Come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:04:00.84,中文,,0,0,0,,可现在，我有点不相信起点和终点了\N{\r英文}But now I'm not so sure I believe in beginnings and endings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:06.00,中文,,0,0,0,,一些和你人生并无交集的日子，却勾勒出你的故事\N{\r英文}There are days that define your story beyond your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.64,中文,,0,0,0,,就好像他们降临的那天\N{\r英文}Like the day they arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.32,中文,,0,0,0,,早上好\N{\r英文}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:23.68,中文,,0,0,0,,- 早上好  - 早上好\N{\r英文}- Morning.  - Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:28.77,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么就你们几个？\N{\r英文}Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:32.88,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧，我们上课吧\N{\r英文}Okay. Well, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.68,中文,,0,0,0,,今天我们谈下葡萄牙语\N{\r英文}Today, we are talking about Portuguese
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:39.85,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么它的发音和其他罗马语系有较大差别\N{\r英文}and why it sounds so different from the other Romance languages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:44.53,中文,,0,0,0,,葡萄牙语发源于加利西亚王国\N{\r英文}The story of Portuguese begins in the kingdom of Galicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:48.44,中文,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉   - 中世纪时期\N{\r英文}- Sorry.  - ...in the Middle Ages,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:53.49,中文,,0,0,0,,语言被视为一种艺术表达方式\N{\r英文}where language was seen as an expression of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.21,中文,,0,0,0,,你有什么新闻想分享吗？\N{\r英文}Any news you wanna share?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:06.12,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士，你能打开电视机，调到新闻频道吗？\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks, can you turn the TV to a news channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:23.56,中文,,0,0,0,,...来到现场\N{\r英文}...arrived here on scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:26.72,中文,,0,0,0,,警察已经在周边区域设置了路障\N{\r英文}but police have already set up a blockade here around the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:29.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以看到，我们已经是尽可能接近了\N{\r英文}As you can see, we've gotten just about as close as we can,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:33.72,中文,,0,0,0,,可遗憾的是，蒙大拿现在已经完全封锁了\N{\r英文}but unfortunately, Montana, right now, is on complete lockdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:39.32,中文,,0,0,0,,40分钟前，不明物体确认着陆在94号州际公路北面\N{\r英文}The object apparently touched down 40 minutes ago just north of I-94.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:43.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我们正等候消息，看这是不是艘实验飞船，又或者...\N{\r英文}We're waiting to hear if this is perhaps an experimental vessel or...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.24,中文,,0,0,0,,等下...\N{\r英文}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:50.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我刚得知，还有更多的这类物体\N{\r英文}I'm learning that more objects like this have landed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:54.28,中文,,0,0,0,,在全球范围内的最少8处地点着陆\N{\r英文}at as many as eight other locations around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:55.64,中文,,0,0,0,,好，我们可以播？\N{\r英文}Yes. Can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:59.76,中文,,0,0,0,,这是北海道某地\N{\r英文}This is from a site in Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:03.08,中文,,0,0,0,,这是此时此刻正在全球发生的事件\N{\r英文}This is worldwide. It is happening right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:11.79,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\r英文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:14.56,中文,,0,0,0,,就到这...  下课了\N{\r英文}That's... Class is dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:05.24,中文,,0,0,0,,目前我们只请求大家的配合\N{\r英文}For now, we're simply asking for cooperation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:07.60,中文,,0,0,0,,等候官方对此物体进行评估\N{\r英文}while authorities assess the object.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:09.28,中文,,0,0,0,,那你就是说它不是我们国家的？\N{\r英文}So, you're saying it's not ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:10.77,中文,,0,0,0,,你根本不知道它是否来自地球吧？\N{\r英文}Do you even know if it's from Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:14.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我们正在收集消息，和其他国家协调\N{\r英文}We're still collecting information. We're coordinating with other countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:18.44,中文,,0,0,0,,不只是我们的后院里冒出这么个东西\N{\r英文}We are not the only ones to have one of these in our backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:21.36,中文,,0,0,0,,如果这是某种寻求和平的第一类接触\N{\r英文}If this is some sort of peaceful first contact,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:23.28,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么要来12艘\N{\r英文}why send 12?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:25.12,中文,,0,0,0,,一艘就够了吧\N{\r英文}Why not just one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:37.64,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯，我知道，我也看到了\N{\r英文}Yeah, I know. I saw that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:52.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道，老妈，我跟你看的新闻都一样\N{\r英文}I don't know, Mom. I'm watching the same news coverage you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:59.40,中文,,0,0,0,,老妈啊，别听那个台胡扯\N{\r英文}Well, Mom, please don't bother with that channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:02.72,中文,,0,0,0,,那些人都是白痴，我提醒过你多少次了？\N{\r英文}How many times do I have to tell you those people are idiots?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:08.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我哪紧张了？\N{\r英文}Yeah, well, do I sound nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.96,中文,,0,0,0,,就是，所以嘛...\N{\r英文}Okay, exactly. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:15.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我？你了解我的，我还不是老样子\N{\r英文}Me? Yeah. You know me, I'm about the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.25,中文,,0,0,0,,老妈，我没事\N{\r英文}Mom, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.76,中文,,0,0,0,,好，我会再打给你的，再见\N{\r英文}Okay, I'll call you later. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.85,中文,,0,0,0,,着陆到现在有差不多8小时了\N{\r英文}And at around eight hours after landing,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:41.08,中文,,0,0,0,,仍旧没有任何"第一类接触"的迹象\N{\r英文}there are still no signs of what might be called "first contact."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:45.00,中文,,0,0,0,,不明物体最少有457米高\N{\r英文}Now, the objects measure at least 1, 500 feet tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.81,中文,,0,0,0,,据报道，还有2艘不明物体进入俄罗斯领空\N{\r英文}Two are reported to have penetrated Russian airspace,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:51.36,中文,,0,0,0,,一艘在西伯利亚，另一艘在黑海沿岸\N{\r英文}one in Siberia and the other off the coast of the Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:52.85,中文,,0,0,0,,矗立在海面上\N{\r英文}...suspended above the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:56.72,中文,,0,0,0,,目前总计有12艘不明物体降落在全球各地\N{\r英文}So far, there are 12 unidentified objects spread across the globe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.53,中文,,0,0,0,,它们的降落地点并无明显关联\N{\r英文}There is no obvious logic to their locations
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:02.16,中文,,0,0,0,,没有证据表明这些飞船是...\N{\r英文}and no evidence that the ships are even...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:05.68,中文,,0,0,0,,如果它的确是某种飞船，也不能排除\N{\r英文}...who entertain the idea that if it is a kind of vessel,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:08.48,中文,,0,0,0,,它是无人驾驶的可能\N{\r英文}it may be unmanned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:12.00,中文,,0,0,0,,不管怎样，我们有应对此类事件的一套方案\N{\r英文}Regardless, we have a protocol for scenarios like this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:24.59,中文,,0,0,0,,委内瑞拉现场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:22.04,中文,,0,0,0,,在经历了不同寻常的周二后\N{\r英文}After Tuesday's extraordinary events,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:25.04,中文,,0,0,0,,总统今早宣布全国进入紧急状态\N{\r英文}the President, this morning, has declared a state of emergency,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:27.88,中文,,0,0,0,,仅蒙大拿州，就有约五千名\N{\r英文}with as many as 5, 000 National Guard being deployed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.80,中文,,0,0,0,,国民警卫队进驻\N{\r英文}to the state of Montana alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.96,中文,,0,0,0,,边境关闭，航班停飞\N{\r英文}Borders are closed and flights have been grounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:33.80,中文,,0,0,0,,上百万旅客滞留机场\N{\r英文}stranding millions of travelers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:37.44,中文,,0,0,0,,人们疯狂抢购汽油，瓶装水和食物\N{\r英文}Panic buying of gas, water, and food continues to escalate
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:40.64,中文,,0,0,0,,联邦政府暂时解除了\N{\r英文}and federal authorities have temporarily lifted all caps
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.96,中文,,0,0,0,,对执法部门的加班禁令\N{\r英文}on overtime for law enforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:46.48,中文,,0,0,0,,烟酒枪械管理署已暂停发放新的持枪许可\N{\r英文}The ATF has put a temporary ban on new gun licenses,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:50.40,中文,,0,0,0,,迫使许多独立供应商抢购各类武器装备\N{\r英文}forcing many independent suppliers of hunting equipment and firearms
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:52.48,中文,,0,0,0,,并把公众拒之门外\N{\r英文}to close their doors to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:55.32,中文,,0,0,0,,48小时过去了，在12个UFO着陆点\N{\r英文}Forty-eight hours later and no further development...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:56.44,中文,,0,0,0,,才2天\N{\r英文}Two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:57.93,中文,,0,0,0,,仍未有新的进展\N{\r英文}...from the sight of the 12 UFO...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:00.60,中文,,0,0,0,,公众就已经指望我们能解答一切了\N{\r英文}And already the public expects us to know the answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:03.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我是GT韦伯上校\N{\r英文}I'm Colonel G.T. Weber.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:06.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我们没有正式见过面\N{\r英文}We never formally met,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:10.00,中文,,0,0,0,,不过2年前，你给情报部门做过波斯语翻译吧？\N{\r英文}but two years ago, you did some Farsi translations for Army intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:13.52,中文,,0,0,0,,那些叛军视频的翻译工作你干得很利索\N{\r英文}You made quick work of those insurgent videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:15.76,中文,,0,0,0,,你跟那些叛军打交道也很利索啊\N{\r英文}You made quick work of those insurgents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:23.04,中文,,0,0,0,,不管是谁推荐翻译专家，都会把你排在最前面\N{\r英文}You are on the top of everyone's list when it comes to translations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:27.36,中文,,0,0,0,,而且你的单一范畴背景调查2年后才失效\N{\r英文}And you have another two years in the SSBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:29.44,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你仍有接触核心机密的许可\N{\r英文}So, you still have top-secret clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:33.16,中文,,0,0,0,,这也是我选择来你办公室，而不是伯克利的原因\N{\r英文}That's why I'm in your office and not at Berkeley.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:35.24,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\r英文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:46.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我有东西想请你翻译\N{\r英文}I have something I need you to translate for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:56.16,中文,,0,0,0,,你们为何而来？\N{\r英文}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:01.80,中文,,0,0,0,,你们听得懂我们的话吗？\N{\r英文}Can you... Can you understand us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:10.85,中文,,0,0,0,,你们来自何方？\N{\r英文}Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:21.41,中文,,0,0,0,,你现在听过了\N{\r英文}Now you heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:23.76,中文,,0,0,0,,有什么想法吗？\N{\r英文}What do you make of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.33,中文,,0,0,0,,那就是...\N{\r英文}Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:30.28,中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\r英文}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.76,中文,,0,0,0,,有几个？\N{\r英文}How many?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.85,中文,,0,0,0,,什么几个？\N{\r英文}How many what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:38.60,中文,,0,0,0,,说话的有几个？\N{\r英文}How many speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:43.60,中文,,0,0,0,,2个\N{\r英文}Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.64,中文,,0,0,0,,假设他们不是同时开口\N{\r英文}Assume they were not speaking at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.56,中文,,0,0,0,,你能肯定？他们有嘴吗？\N{\r英文}Are you sure? Did they have mouths...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:54.53,中文,,0,0,0,,你会如何来翻译这个？\N{\r英文}How would you approach translating this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:57.53,中文,,0,0,0,,你能分辨出词语\N{\r英文}Do you hear any words?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:12:59.32,中文,,0,0,0,,或者句子吗？\N{\r英文}Phrases?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:03.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我，我不知道\N{\r英文}I don't... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:06.05,中文,,0,0,0,,那你能告诉我什么？\N{\r英文}So, what can you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:10.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我能告诉你的是，仅凭一个音频文件是做不出翻译的\N{\r英文}I can tell you that it's impossible to translate from an audio file.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:12.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我得亲历现场与他们交谈\N{\r英文}I would need to be there to interact with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:16.72,中文,,0,0,0,,你翻译波斯语时也没在现场啊\N{\r英文}You didn't need that with the Farsi translations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:18.64,中文,,0,0,0,,那是因为我已经掌握了波斯语\N{\r英文}I didn't need it because I already knew the language.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:20.76,中文,,0,0,0,,而这个...\N{\r英文}But this, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:26.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你打的什么主意\N{\r英文}I know what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:28.96,中文,,0,0,0,,- 揭穿我啊  - 我不会带你去蒙大拿\N{\r英文}- Tell me what I'm doing.  - I'm not taking you to Montana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:31.28,中文,,0,0,0,,能接触核心机密的人多了，我不会让那变成\N{\r英文}It's all I can do to keep it from turning into a tourist site
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:32.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你们的旅游景点\N{\r英文}for everybody who has a TS clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:35.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我只是跟你讲明如何才能做好这份工作\N{\r英文}I'm just telling you what it would take to do this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:37.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我不是来跟你讨价还价的\N{\r英文}This is not a negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:41.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我出了这个门，你的机会就没了\N{\r英文}If I leave here, your chance is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.52,中文,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\r英文}Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.60,中文,,0,0,0,,上校\N{\r英文}Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:58.68,中文,,0,0,0,,你刚提到了伯克利，你接下来要找丹弗斯吧？\N{\r英文}You mentioned Berkeley, are you going to ask Danvers next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:13:59.76,中文,,0,0,0,,可能吧\N{\r英文}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:02.36,中文,,0,0,0,,在你邀请他前\N{\r英文}Before you commit to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:05.84,中文,,0,0,0,,问他梵文里的“战争”一词，以及翻译过来的意思\N{\r英文}ask him the Sanskrit word for "war" and its translation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:17.64,中文,,0,0,0,,在中国和俄罗斯加入联合国的磋商后\N{\r英文}An agreement on sharing scientific discoveries looks closer tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:20.80,中文,,0,0,0,,有望就共享科学发现达成协议\N{\r英文}as Russia and China join talks at the United Nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:24.88,中文,,0,0,0,,以此同时，全球金融市场陷入危机\N{\r英文}Meanwhile, financial markets across the world are in crisis
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:28.80,中文,,0,0,0,,道琼斯工业指数狂泻2000点\N{\r英文}as the Dow Jones Industrial Average fell over 2,000 points
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:31.28,中文,,0,0,0,,打破了一周跌幅的历史记录\N{\r英文}in its worst weekly decline in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:47.24,中文,,0,0,0,,早上好\N{\r英文}Mornin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.44,中文,,0,0,0,,上校\N{\r英文}Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:52.49,中文,,0,0,0,,“加维什提” 他说是争论的意思\N{\r英文}Gavisti. He says it means "an argument."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:53.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你的标准答案是？\N{\r英文}What do you say it means?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.48,中文,,0,0,0,,寻找更多的牛\N{\r英文}"A desire for more cows."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.56,中文,,0,0,0,,收拾好背包\N{\r英文}Pack your bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.36,中文,,0,0,0,,好的，给我20分钟\N{\r英文}All right, give me 20 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:01.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我们10分钟后起飞\N{\r英文}We take off in 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:05.48,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士，请跟我来\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks. Right this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.52,中文,,0,0,0,,准备起飞\N{\r英文}Contact and ready to approach...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:25.08,中文,,0,0,0,,不好意思，班克斯博士，让我检查下你的安全带\N{\r英文}Excuse me, Dr. Banks, let me make sure you're properly secured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:34.60,中文,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\r英文}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:12.84,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\r英文}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.96,0:16:17.96,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉，刚才听不清你说了什么\N{\r英文}Sorry, I couldn't hear what you were saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:21.61,中文,,0,0,0,,语言是文明的基石\N{\r英文}"Language is the foundation of civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:24.28,中文,,0,0,0,,是把人们聚到一起的粘合剂\N{\r英文}"It is the glue that holds a people together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:26.72,中文,,0,0,0,,也是冲突中最先使用的武器\N{\r英文}"It is the first weapon drawn in a conflict."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:30.76,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝，这位是伊恩·唐纳利\N{\r英文}Louise, this is Ian Donnelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.49,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝·班克斯，伊恩·唐纳利\N{\r英文}Louise Banks, Ian Donnelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:33.60,中文,,0,0,0,,这个见面礼不错嘛\N{\r英文}It's quite a greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:35.24,中文,,0,0,0,,是啊，你的大作\N{\r英文}Yeah. Well, you wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:36.76,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯，不过\N{\r英文}Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:39.60,中文,,0,0,0,,序言都是这么写的\N{\r英文}It's the kind of thing you write as a preface,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:41.60,中文,,0,0,0,,言简意赅，博取眼球\N{\r英文}dazzle them with the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:43.57,中文,,0,0,0,,话是漂亮\N{\r英文}Yeah. It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:44.92,中文,,0,0,0,,可惜说错了\N{\r英文}Even if it's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.20,中文,,0,0,0,,错了？\N{\r英文}It's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:50.80,中文,,0,0,0,,文明的基石并不是语言，而是科学\N{\r英文}Well, the cornerstone of civilization isn't language, it's science.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:55.20,中文,,0,0,0,,伊恩是阿拉莫斯国家实验室的理论物理学家\N{\r英文}Ian is a theoretical physicist from Los Alamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:58.52,中文,,0,0,0,,你向我汇报工作，不过在“蛋壳”里时，你会和他搭配工作\N{\r英文}You'll be reporting to me, but you'll be working with him when you're in the shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:01.68,中文,,0,0,0,,他们是这样叫不明飞行物的？\N{\r英文}That's what they're calling the UFO.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:05.28,中文,,0,0,0,,首要任务，搞清他们来自何方，来这里的目的\N{\r英文}Priority one. What do they want, where are they from.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.68,中文,,0,0,0,,除此之外，他们是如何过来的\N{\r英文}And beyond that, how did they get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:10.20,中文,,0,0,0,,他们掌握了超光速旅行吗？\N{\r英文}Are they capable of faster-than-light travel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:11.32,中文,,0,0,0,,他们...\N{\r英文}Are they...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:14.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我专门列了个问题的单子，可以跟你说下\N{\r英文}I have a list of questions that, you know, we can go over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:17.49,中文,,0,0,0,,先用二进制序列来欢迎他们\N{\r英文}Starting with a series of just a "handshake" of binary sequences...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:19.05,中文,,0,0,0,,先别急着问他们各种数学问题\N{\r英文}How about we just talk to them
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:21.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我们从简单交流开始，好吗？\N{\r英文}before we start throwing math problems at them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:25.60,中文,,0,0,0,,这正是要你们两个的原因\N{\r英文}This is why you're both here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:29.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我负责端咖啡\N{\r英文}I'll bring the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:33.40,中文,,0,0,0,,跟外星人一起喝咖啡\N{\r英文}Coffee with some aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:46.92,中文,,0,0,0,,带他们两个去凯特勒博士那\N{\r英文}All right. I want you to take these two to Dr. Kettler.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.04,中文,,0,0,0,,遵命，长官\N{\r英文}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:49.64,中文,,0,0,0,,跟这位上尉去医务室\N{\r英文}Follow the captain to Medical.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:52.60,中文,,0,0,0,,要花几分钟走下程序，之后我们就开工了\N{\r英文}The procedure should take just a few minutes, and then, we'll get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:06.36,中文,,0,0,0,,背包就交给他们保管吧\N{\r英文}These men are gonna take care of your bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:07.64,中文,,0,0,0,,手机交给我\N{\r英文}I'll take your cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:09.44,中文,,0,0,0,,手机\N{\r英文}Cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.04,中文,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\r英文}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:14.84,中文,,0,0,0,,带上这个，任何时候都别取\N{\r英文}Put these on. You're gonna wear them at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:25.20,中文,,0,0,0,,- 他们来了再说  - 很好\N{\r英文}- Not until they're here.  - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:30.08,中文,,0,0,0,,长官，他们来了\N{\r英文}Sir, they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.84,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝·班克斯，伊恩·唐纳利\N{\r英文}Louise Banks? Ian Donnelly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.48,中文,,0,0,0,,你们上一次用餐是什么时候？\N{\r英文}When was the last time either of you have eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.24,中文,,0,0,0,,- 昨晚  - 我也一样\N{\r英文}- Last night.  - Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.32,0:20:37.76,中文,,0,0,0,,你们上一次做有精神压力的事，是什么时候？\N{\r英文}When's the last time you did something stressful?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:39.48,中文,,0,0,0,,现在算吗？\N{\r英文}Does now count?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.40,中文,,0,0,0,,说说而已\N{\r英文}Just saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:46.24,中文,,0,0,0,,刚刚被抬进救伤直升机的是谁？\N{\r英文}Who was being carted off in the medevac?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:49.13,中文,,0,0,0,,不是每个人都能承受这种经历\N{\r英文}Not everyone is able to process experiences like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:51.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我需要给你们抽点血\N{\r英文}I'm gonna get some blood from you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:54.48,中文,,0,0,0,,然后再给你们打一针疫苗，来抵御各类细菌威胁\N{\r英文}and give you an immunization dose that covers a battery of bacterial threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:55.92,中文,,0,0,0,,你们能签下这个吗？\N{\r英文}Would you sign these, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:57.24,中文,,0,0,0,,请把袖子卷起来\N{\r英文}And roll up your sleeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.28,0:20:59.48,中文,,0,0,0,,你们都没有幽闭恐惧症吧？\N{\r英文}Either of you claustrophobic?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:00.89,中文,,0,0,0,,- 没有  - 没\N{\r英文}- Nope.  - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:05.04,中文,,0,0,0,,有在服用什么药吗？对什么过敏吗？怀孕呢？\N{\r英文}Currently taking any medications? Allergies? Pregnant?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:06.76,中文,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\r英文}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:08.80,中文,,0,0,0,,加强剂的药效明显\N{\r英文}The booster is a kick to your system,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:10.60,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你们可能会有不良反应\N{\r英文}so you may experience some side-effects,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:12.76,中文,,0,0,0,,诸如恶心，头晕，头疼\N{\r英文}nausea, dizziness, headaches,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.84,0:21:15.32,中文,,0,0,0,,或者耳鸣之类的\N{\r英文}a ringing in your ears like you have tinnitus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:28.45,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道他怎么了吗？\N{\r英文}You see what's happening to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:29.80,中文,,0,0,0,,这个怎么可能？\N{\r英文}How does this even work?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:31.80,中文,,0,0,0,,读数并无变化，不过...\N{\r英文}The readings do not change, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:34.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我也搞不懂，我们像是爬在纸上的昆虫\N{\r英文}I don't know. It's like we're insects on a piece of paper
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:37.04,中文,,0,0,0,,然后他们让我们自己滚蛋\N{\r英文}and they're easing us out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:40.12,中文,,0,0,0,,在112分钟19秒后\N{\r英文}At exactly 112 minutes and 19 seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:43.64,中文,,0,0,0,,重力开始回升，让我们慢慢滑出房间\N{\r英文}the gravity starts to shift and slides us out of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:46.61,中文,,0,0,0,,对此你能做出科学上的解释吗？\N{\r英文}Have you found a scientific explanation for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:48.72,中文,,0,0,0,,比如这个变化是为了他们自己？\N{\r英文}Like, is it for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:50.00,中文,,0,0,0,,不，我觉得是照顾我们\N{\r英文}No, we think it's for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:52.80,中文,,0,0,0,,似乎房间内的空气并不流通\N{\r英文}The air doesn't seem to circulate inside the chamber,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.88,0:21:55.80,中文,,0,0,0,,所以顶多两小时，氧气就耗尽了\N{\r英文}so after about two hours, you run out of oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:59.32,中文,,0,0,0,,那输送新鲜空气进房间，18个小时还不够吗？\N{\r英文}It doesn't take 18 hours to pump fresh air into a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:00.52,中文,,0,0,0,,大气\N{\r英文}Atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:03.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你说什么？\N{\r英文}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.72,0:22:06.16,中文,,0,0,0,,如果他们的大气和地球上的不同\N{\r英文}If their atmosphere is different from Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:07.68,中文,,0,0,0,,那他们每次打开大门前\N{\r英文}it would certainly take hours
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:10.96,中文,,0,0,0,,就肯定需要数小时来制造适宜氧气浓度和压力来照顾我们\N{\r英文}to rebalance the O2 content and pressure for us every time they open their door.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.32,0:22:14.40,中文,,0,0,0,,照你这么说，他们随时都可以闷死我们？\N{\r英文}So, you're saying they could suffocate us if they wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:16.40,中文,,0,0,0,,这位是大卫·哈尔彭，中情局的特工\N{\r英文}This is Agent David Halpern with the CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:19.16,中文,,0,0,0,,跟我去你们的工作地点吧\N{\r英文}Let me get you two to your stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.24,0:22:20.20,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\r英文}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.28,0:22:22.80,中文,,0,0,0,,记住，我们必须尽快搞清这些问题\N{\r英文}Remember, we need answers as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:26.00,中文,,0,0,0,,他们来做什么，他们来自何方，他们来这的目的\N{\r英文}What do they want, where are they from, why they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:27.52,中文,,0,0,0,,- 这是首先要解决的  - 好\N{\r英文}- This is the priority.  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:31.52,中文,,0,0,0,,大家，这位是伊恩·唐纳利博士，他负责带你们队\N{\r英文}Everyone, this is Dr. Ian Donnelly. He'll be running this team here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.60,0:22:33.80,中文,,0,0,0,,他们有对什么做出回应吗\N{\r英文}Yeah, have they responded to anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.88,0:22:36.36,中文,,0,0,0,,形状，模式，数字，斐波那契数列？\N{\r英文}Shapes, patterns, numbers, Fibonacci?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:38.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我们并不懂他们说的话，不过他们对“你好”有回应\N{\r英文}We can't tell what they are saying when they respond to "hello,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.60,0:22:41.60,中文,,0,0,0,,别急于求成就行\N{\r英文}so don't get ahead of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:45.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你现在有收获吗？\N{\r英文}What have you figured out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.04,0:22:47.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我们才刚开始而已\N{\r英文}We're just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:49.32,中文,,0,0,0,,- 早上好各位  - 早上好\N{\r英文}- Good morning.  - Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.40,0:22:51.12,中文,,0,0,0,,这位是路易丝·班克斯博士\N{\r英文}This is Dr. Louise Banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:52.24,中文,,0,0,0,,她负责带你们队\N{\r英文}She'll be heading your team.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.32,0:22:54.08,中文,,0,0,0,,- 班克斯博士，很荣幸  - 你好\N{\r英文}- Dr. Banks. It's a pleasure meeting you.  - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:56.32,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士会接手沃勒博士的工作\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks is taking over the mission from Dr. Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.40,0:22:58.32,中文,,0,0,0,,- 很高兴见面  - 班克斯博士，很高兴你能来\N{\r英文}- Nice to see you.  - Dr. Banks, glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.40,0:23:00.44,中文,,0,0,0,,这是15分钟警报\N{\r英文}That's your 15-minute warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.12,0:23:02.56,中文,,0,0,0,,你以前潜过水吗？\N{\r英文}You scuba-dive before?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:07.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要进入何种辐射环境？\N{\r英文}What kind of radiation exposure are we walking into?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:09.88,中文,,0,0,0,,正常水平，这些只是以防万一\N{\r英文}Nominal, these are just for safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:13.00,中文,,0,0,0,,如果有任何身体接触\N{\r英文}So, is there any physical contact with the...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:16.12,中文,,0,0,0,,有谁跟我一样讲不出“外星人”吗？\N{\r英文}Am I the only one having trouble saying "aliens"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.20,0:23:19.01,中文,,0,0,0,,有堵墙，玻璃状的，你没法接近他们\N{\r英文}There's a wall, like a glass wall. You can't get to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:22.32,中文,,0,0,0,,那他们长啥样的？\N{\r英文}So, what do they look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:25.52,中文,,0,0,0,,你马上就知道了，动作快点吧\N{\r英文}You'll see soon enough. Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:28.12,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢，请走这边\N{\r英文}Thank you. Turn this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:36.20,中文,,0,0,0,,全体人员，等候指令，完毕\N{\r英文}All units, stand by. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:49.00,中文,,0,0,0,,刚穿防护服可能行动不便，不过你们会适应的\N{\r英文}The suits are clumsy at first, but you get used to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.32,0:23:52.84,中文,,0,0,0,,放到第二辆车上\N{\r英文}Load up in the second vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:55.80,中文,,0,0,0,,快点，快点，放到这里\N{\r英文}Hurry up, hurry up. Bring it over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.88,0:23:56.88,中文,,0,0,0,,都搬完了，长官\N{\r英文}We're clear over here, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.00,0:23:59.24,中文,,0,0,0,,所有设备，长官，这是最后一箱了，这辆车可以走了\N{\r英文}All set, sir. This is the last box for this truck. This truck's clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.52,0:24:00.52,中文,,0,0,0,,出发\N{\r英文}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:02.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我们几分钟后到\N{\r英文}We'll be there in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:04.37,中文,,0,0,0,,都坐稳抓牢了\N{\r英文}Make sure you hold on to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.16,0:24:12.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我们已进入非军事区\N{\r英文}We are now inside the demilitarized zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.52,0:24:15.33,中文,,0,0,0,,- 距离1.2公里，完毕  - 收到，A小队\N{\r英文}- Raise 1.2 klicks. Over.  - Copy, Alpha.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.40,0:24:19.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我们会继续监视生命体征，以及行动中的各种信号强度\N{\r英文}We'll continue to monitor vitals and signal clarity from operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.36,0:24:21.80,中文,,0,0,0,,预警机已就位，运转正常\N{\r英文}Airpicket's in position and fully operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.88,0:24:24.32,中文,,0,0,0,,反制措施已就位，等候指令，完毕\N{\r英文}Countermeasures in place and ready for deployment. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.76,0:25:04.24,中文,,0,0,0,,收到，秃鹫，我们只进行观察，不会贸然采取行动，完毕\N{\r英文}Copy, Condor. We will observe, but not initiate. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.84,0:25:05.92,中文,,0,0,0,,小心\N{\r英文}Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.24,0:25:09.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我们会保持频道畅通，完毕\N{\r英文}We'll keep Alpha channel open. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.60,0:25:12.33,中文,,0,0,0,,A小队，请注意，湿度比昨天有所提高\N{\r英文}Alpha, be advised. Humidity increased since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.40,0:25:13.68,中文,,0,0,0,,每隔18小时\N{\r英文}Every 18 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.56,0:25:16.28,中文,,0,0,0,,飞船底部会打开扇门\N{\r英文}the door opens up at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.12,0:25:20.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我们就从那进去\N{\r英文}That's where we go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.52,0:25:24.04,中文,,0,0,0,,红队已做好准备\N{\r英文}Red team on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.24,0:25:33.24,中文,,0,0,0,,一切正常，A小队，可以行动，完毕\N{\r英文}Zero movement. Alpha detail, clear to proceed. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.56,0:25:36.53,中文,,0,0,0,,收到，秃鹫，我们上去了，完毕\N{\r英文}Copy, Condor. Beginning our ascent now Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.44,0:25:43.44,中文,,0,0,0,,3米\N{\r英文}Ten feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.88,0:25:49.29,中文,,0,0,0,,1.5米\N{\r英文}Five feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.80,0:25:53.37,中文,,0,0,0,,0.7米 0.3米\N{\r英文}Two. One.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.00,0:26:13.68,中文,,0,0,0,,A小队，准许进入通道，完毕\N{\r英文}Alpha, clear to enter antechamber. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.52,0:26:23.72,中文,,0,0,0,,收到，秃鹫，正在前进，完毕\N{\r英文}Copy, Condor. Moving into position. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.76,0:26:35.56,中文,,0,0,0,,离目标还有9米\N{\r英文}Thirty feet from target.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.64,0:26:39.36,中文,,0,0,0,,有不明干扰，不过遥测装置工作正常，完毕\N{\r英文}Suit telemetry now full strength, despite unknown interference. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.60,0:26:49.36,中文,,0,0,0,,1.5米 0.7米 0.3米\N{\r英文}Five feet. Two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.04,0:27:15.56,中文,,0,0,0,,氧气浓度20.3%，未检测到污染物，完毕\N{\r英文}Oxygen level, 20.3%. No known contaminates. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.84,0:27:16.88,中文,,0,0,0,,生命体征正常\N{\r英文}Vitals normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.12,0:27:20.92,中文,,0,0,0,,重力0.97G\N{\r英文}Gravity at 0. 97.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.68,0:27:31.80,中文,,0,0,0,,无线电信号减弱\N{\r英文}Radio signal strength decreasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.92,0:27:35.40,中文,,0,0,0,,90%, 85%，波动中\N{\r英文}90%. 85%. Fluctuating...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.44,0:27:55.16,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯，这也行\N{\r英文}Yeah, that just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.68,0:28:18.68,中文,,0,0,0,,好了，出发吧，时间不等人\N{\r英文}All right, let's move. Time is wasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.80,0:28:21.20,中文,,0,0,0,,你准备好了？你呢？\N{\r英文}You ready? You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.08,0:28:23.36,中文,,0,0,0,,我们上吧\N{\r英文}Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.44,0:28:26.80,中文,,0,0,0,,秃鹫，我和马克上尉先进去了，完毕\N{\r英文}Condor, I'm proceeding first with Captain Marks. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.56,0:28:33.04,中文,,0,0,0,,无线电信号强度75%，完毕\N{\r英文}Radio signal strength 75%. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.12,0:28:36.01,中文,,0,0,0,,已落地，通道里重力微弱，完毕\N{\r英文}Landed. Gravity nominal in the antechamber. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.08,0:28:39.20,中文,,0,0,0,,一切正常，长官\N{\r英文}It's all good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.36,0:28:41.12,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你可以上来了  - 准备接应\N{\r英文}- You can proceed.  - Stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.72,0:28:42.96,中文,,0,0,0,,好了，上来吧\N{\r英文}Okay, bring it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.80,0:28:49.80,中文,,0,0,0,,生命体征正常\N{\r英文}Vitals in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.88,0:28:53.48,中文,,0,0,0,,无线电信号强度稳定在75%，完毕\N{\r英文}Radio signal strength stable at 75%. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.24,0:28:56.40,中文,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？\N{\r英文}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.64,0:29:00.64,中文,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\r英文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.00,0:29:03.16,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.56,0:29:08.84,中文,,0,0,0,,你能行的，去吧\N{\r英文}You can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.48,0:29:10.48,中文,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\r英文}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.84,0:29:13.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道... 我觉得...\N{\r英文}I don't know, I... I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.44,0:29:22.44,中文,,0,0,0,,接住她\N{\r英文}Grab her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.56,0:29:37.56,中文,,0,0,0,,唐纳利博士，你没事吧？\N{\r英文}Dr. Donnelly, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.52,0:29:40.68,中文,,0,0,0,,唐纳利博士，你没事吧？\N{\r英文}Dr. Donnelly. You good?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.44,0:29:46.28,中文,,0,0,0,,唐纳利博士，你没事吧？请回答，完毕\N{\r英文}Dr. Donnelly, are you all right? Please respond. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.76,0:29:47.76,中文,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\r英文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.36,0:29:52.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\r英文}Holy fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.24,0:30:00.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我们去那里面\N{\r英文}We're gonna go down there,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.52,0:30:02.09,中文,,0,0,0,,你们就可以开工了\N{\r英文}and you're gonna start your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.16,0:30:03.16,中文,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\r英文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.40,0:30:05.40,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好了？全体前进  - 好的\N{\r英文}- Okay? Everybody, move out.  - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.12,0:30:08.04,中文,,0,0,0,,A小队已就位\N{\r英文}Alpha detail is in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.20,0:30:09.64,中文,,0,0,0,,小队已就位\N{\r英文}Team is in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.04,0:30:11.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我们进去了\N{\r英文}We're on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.16,0:30:59.32,中文,,0,0,0,,秃鹫，A队已进入房间\N{\r英文}Condor, Alpha's now in the nave.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.76,0:31:02.12,中文,,0,0,0,,布置设备和遥测装置，完毕\N{\r英文}Setting up equipment and telemetry. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.20,0:31:24.77,中文,,0,0,0,,氧气浓度21.3%，完毕\N{\r英文}Oxygen level, 21.3%. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.92,0:31:37.57,中文,,0,0,0,,下面做什么？\N{\r英文}So, what happens now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.60,0:31:41.96,中文,,0,0,0,,等他们现身\N{\r英文}They arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.04,0:32:47.20,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士？\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.52,0:32:53.68,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士？\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.84,0:32:57.20,中文,,0,0,0,,可以开始了\N{\r英文}You can start.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.12,0:33:02.09,中文,,0,0,0,,A小队，请直接前往污染物净化室\N{\r英文}Alpha detail, proceed directly through the decontamination...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.16,0:33:03.60,中文,,0,0,0,,穿过气密门\N{\r英文}...to the inner airlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.68,0:33:07.28,中文,,0,0,0,,在通过气密门前不要停下\N{\r英文}Do not stop until you have passed through the airlock doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.36,0:33:09.32,中文,,0,0,0,,没有正规人员的专业协助\N{\r英文}Do not attempt to remove the hazmat suit
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.40,0:33:12.00,中文,,0,0,0,,不要自行脱下核生化防护服\N{\r英文}without proper assistance of authorized personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.08,0:33:15.76,中文,,0,0,0,,重复，不要自行脱下核生化防护服\N{\r英文}Repeat. Hazmat suits without assistance of authorized personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.84,0:33:18.00,中文,,0,0,0,,- 等等，稍等一下  - 好了\N{\r英文}- Wait, just a minute. A minute. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.08,0:33:19.44,中文,,0,0,0,,把你的头低下\N{\r英文}Keep your head low.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.20,0:33:32.16,中文,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\r英文}Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.28,0:33:33.69,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好了  - 请站出来吧\N{\r英文}- All right.  - Step on out, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.96,0:33:34.96,中文,,0,0,0,,扶着那\N{\r英文}Now hold that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.56,0:33:39.56,中文,,0,0,0,,要我走人吗？\N{\r英文}Am I fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.28,0:33:41.61,中文,,0,0,0,,你表现不错，比上一位强\N{\r英文}You did better than the last guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.36,0:33:45.52,中文,,0,0,0,,可我还是高兴不起来\N{\r英文}That doesn't make me feel any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.72,0:33:50.04,中文,,0,0,0,,你们在凌晨两点前要拿出方案来\N{\r英文}You both have till 0200 hours to figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.12,0:33:51.28,中文,,0,0,0,,好，那之后呢\N{\r英文}Okay, what happens then?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.44,0:33:53.80,中文,,0,0,0,,你又回去\N{\r英文}You go back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.28,0:34:31.09,中文,,0,0,0,,UFO降临事件持续发酵\N{\r英文}Violence continues to spread across the US today
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.16,0:34:33.00,中文,,0,0,0,,美国各地今日继续爆发各种骚乱\N{\r英文}in the wake of the 12 landings.
