Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.00,0:34:51.92,中文,,0,0,0,,他们的网站上宣称，外星人的降临\N{\r英文}Their website claims the arrival of the aliens
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.00,0:34:56.76,中文,,0,0,0,,印证了启示录14:1-5，信徒应当响应\N{\r英文}set in motion a prophecy that 12 sets of 12 should "follow the lamb."
