Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.44,0:35:25.20,中文,,0,0,0,,他们播放音频回应我们时，声源不明\N{\r英文}Well, they play audio back at us from an unseen source.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.44,0:35:27.64,中文,,0,0,0,,什么音频？\N{\r英文}Audio of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.20,0:35:32.64,中文,,0,0,0,,就房间里的一些谈话，还有对话里的随机片段\N{\r英文}It's bits of conversation from the room, random clips of dialogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.72,0:35:35.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我们一无所获\N{\r英文}Really, we... We have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.96,0:35:41.96,中文,,0,0,0,,距“蛋壳”开启还有14分钟\N{\r英文}T-minus 14 minutes to shell access.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.36,0:35:43.72,中文,,0,0,0,,你收到我的信号了吗？\N{\r英文}Are you receiving my signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.40,0:35:45.56,中文,,0,0,0,,收到了，正在发送\N{\r英文}Yes. It's sending.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.64,0:35:47.64,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好，谢谢  - 好的，希望你有收获\N{\r英文}- Okay, thanks.  - Okay. Good hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.72,0:35:48.68,中文,,0,0,0,,出发了\N{\r英文}Heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.76,0:35:50.25,中文,,0,0,0,,检查无线电，听得到我说话吗？\N{\r英文}Checking in for radio. Are you receiving me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.88,0:35:52.24,中文,,0,0,0,,你的声音宏亮清晰\N{\r英文}You're coming in loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.08,0:35:55.08,中文,,0,0,0,,祝你好运，博士\N{\r英文}Good luck, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.48,0:36:02.18,中文,,0,0,0,,氧气瓶状态：1到6皆满
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.68,0:36:10.52,中文,,0,0,0,,距“蛋壳”开启还有9分钟\N{\r英文}T-minus nine minutes to shell access.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.60,0:36:11.84,中文,,0,0,0,,那个做什么用的？\N{\r英文}What's that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.20,0:36:13.44,中文,,0,0,0,,涂写用的视觉教具\N{\r英文}A visual aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.72,0:36:18.32,中文,,0,0,0,,听着，他们不开口的话，我一辈子都甭想学会他们的语言\N{\r英文}Look, I'm never going to be able to speak their words if they are talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.40,0:36:23.68,中文,,0,0,0,,可要是他们有文字之类的，或简单的视觉交流方式\N{\r英文}But they might have some sort of written language or basis for visual communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.76,0:36:25.68,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧，让我们试试\N{\r英文}Okay. Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.96,0:36:37.00,中文,,0,0,0,,人类\N{\r英文}Human.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.16,0:37:06.16,中文,,0,0,0,,人类\N{\r英文}"Human."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.16,0:37:11.44,中文,,0,0,0,,我是人类\N{\r英文}I'm human.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.80,0:37:14.00,中文,,0,0,0,,你是什么？\N{\r英文}What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.44,0:37:26.64,中文,,0,0,0,,人类\N{\r英文}Human.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.84,0:38:15.88,中文,,0,0,0,,收到，A队\N{\r英文}Affirmative, Alpha...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.08,0:38:18.08,中文,,0,0,0,,- 天啊\N{\r英文}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.40,0:38:19.73,中文,,0,0,0,,你录下来了吗？\N{\r英文}Are you getting this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.84,0:38:21.80,中文,,0,0,0,,是的，长官，正传回大本营\N{\r英文}Yes, sir. It's uploading back to base camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.44,0:38:24.44,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.24,0:38:26.65,中文,,0,0,0,,这真是难以置信啊\N{\r英文}That's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.88,0:38:41.88,中文,,0,0,0,,人类\N{\r英文}Human.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.48,0:38:45.52,中文,,0,0,0,,人类\N{\r英文}Human.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.08,0:38:48.08,中文,,0,0,0,,人类\N{\r英文}Human.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.76,0:39:00.84,中文,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\r英文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.20,0:39:02.53,中文,,0,0,0,,很好... 慢点啊，伙计\N{\r英文}Okay, slow down, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.52,0:39:04.52,中文,,0,0,0,,慢点\N{\r英文}Slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.96,0:39:24.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我不是想否认你取得的成果\N{\r英文}I don't wanna take away from your success in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.48,0:39:26.96,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士，就只有这一招了吗？\N{\r英文}but, Dr. Banks, is this really the right approach?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.44,0:39:30.88,中文,,0,0,0,,交他们读书认字？\N{\r英文}Trying to teach 'em how to speak and read?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.96,0:39:32.12,中文,,0,0,0,,这得花多久啊\N{\r英文}That's gotta take longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.20,0:39:34.77,中文,,0,0,0,,你不懂，这会事半功倍的\N{\r英文}You're wrong. It's faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.72,0:39:41.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你在这里做的每件事，我都要给一屋子的人解释\N{\r英文}Everything you do in there I have to explain to a room full of men
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.44,0:39:45.52,中文,,0,0,0,,而他们只关心一个问题：“这会给我们带来怎样的麻烦”\N{\r英文}whose first and last question is, "How can this be used against us?"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.88,0:39:48.48,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你得给我令人信服的理由\N{\r英文}So, you're gonna have to give me more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.96,0:39:51.37,中文,,0,0,0,,袋鼠\N{\r英文}Kangaroo.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.44,0:39:53.85,中文,,0,0,0,,什么意思？\N{\r英文}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.92,0:39:55.33,中文,,0,0,0,,1770年\N{\r英文}In 1770,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.40,0:39:58.72,中文,,0,0,0,,船长詹姆斯·库克的船只在澳大利亚沿岸搁浅\N{\r英文}Captain James Cook's ship ran aground off the coast of Australia,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.80,0:40:02.40,中文,,0,0,0,,他带队登陆，并见到了当地的土著\N{\r英文}and he led a party into the country and they met the Aboriginal people.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.48,0:40:05.52,中文,,0,0,0,,其中一位水手指着把幼崽装在兜里\N{\r英文}One of the sailors pointed at the animals that hop around
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.60,0:40:07.36,中文,,0,0,0,,在地上蹦来蹦去的动物\N{\r英文}and put their babies in their pouch,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.44,0:40:10.25,中文,,0,0,0,,问它们叫什么，土著回答“Kanguru”\N{\r英文}and he asked what they were, and the Aborigines said, "Kanguru."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.12,0:40:14.36,中文,,0,0,0,,你想表明什么？\N{\r英文}And the point is?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.68,0:40:18.52,中文,,0,0,0,,很久以后他们才搞懂“Kanguru”的意思是“我听不懂”\N{\r英文}It wasn't until later that they learned that "kanguru" means "I don't understand."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.60,0:40:22.24,中文,,0,0,0,,所以，我在房间里用这个是为了化解误会\N{\r英文}So, I need this so that we don't misinterpret things in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.32,0:40:25.16,中文,,0,0,0,,不然得耗费10倍的时间\N{\r英文}otherwise this is gonna take 10 times as long.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.76,0:40:28.56,中文,,0,0,0,,这理由勉强能交差\N{\r英文}I could sell that for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.68,0:40:31.72,中文,,0,0,0,,下次对话前，你必须把要用的词\N{\r英文}But I need you to submit your vocabulary words
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.80,0:40:32.88,中文,,0,0,0,,拟个单子给我\N{\r英文}before the next session.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.52,0:40:34.48,中文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\r英文}Fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.56,0:40:37.16,中文,,0,0,0,,请别忘了土著人的遭遇\N{\r英文}And remember what happened to the Aborigines.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.48,0:40:40.80,中文,,0,0,0,,一个更先进的种族差点令他们灭亡\N{\r英文}A more advanced race nearly wiped 'em out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.52,0:40:50.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你讲的故事不错\N{\r英文}It's a good story.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.40,0:40:51.52,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\r英文}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.36,0:40:53.88,中文,,0,0,0,,是杜撰的\N{\r英文}It's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.96,0:40:55.80,中文,,0,0,0,,但管用就行\N{\r英文}But it proves my point.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.79,0:41:09.99,中文,,0,0,0,,人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.44,0:41:15.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们能还原出\N{\r英文}We think we were able to reproduce
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.40,0:41:18.00,中文,,0,0,0,,一些素数序列给他们\N{\r英文}some prime number sequences back at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.12,0:41:19.24,中文,,0,0,0,,也算是有收获\N{\r英文}So, that's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.32,0:41:21.36,中文,,0,0,0,,祝贺你，学到鹦鹉的本事了\N{\r英文}Well, congratulations. You're a parrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.44,0:41:23.96,中文,,0,0,0,,意义远不止如此，你个自大狂\N{\r英文}Well, it's a lot more than that, you cheeky bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.04,0:41:26.96,中文,,0,0,0,,装糊涂吗？他们似乎搞不懂我们的几何学\N{\r英文}Don't you see? They can't seem to follow our algebra.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.40,0:41:31.08,中文,,0,0,0,,反而对高深点的，更有共鸣\N{\r英文}But complex behaviors? That clicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.44,0:41:37.33,中文,,0,0,0,,这根本没道理啊，不是吗？\N{\r英文}Well, that doesn't make any sense at all, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.20,0:41:45.72,中文,,0,0,0,,问题是，不是每个人都认同我们和外星人开诚布公的做法\N{\r英文}The problem is, not everyone shares our policy of being open with the aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.80,0:41:47.40,中文,,0,0,0,,这位是尚将军\N{\r英文}Have you met General Shang?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.92,0:41:50.36,中文,,0,0,0,,他主宰着局势走向\N{\r英文}Call sign for him is "Big Domino."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.44,0:41:53.84,中文,,0,0,0,,不管尚做什么，最少也会有4个国家效仿\N{\r英文}Whatever Shang does, at least four other nations will follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.92,0:41:56.57,中文,,0,0,0,,- 路易丝，我们今天休整一下  - 好\N{\r英文}- Louise, you have to gain ground today.  - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.64,0:41:59.21,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你给我准备好词语单了吗？  - 准备好了\N{\r英文}- You have a vocabulary list for me?  - I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.04,0:42:08.24,中文,,0,0,0,,你要教他们认识你和伊恩的名字？\N{\r英文}You're gonna teach them your name and Ian's?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.32,0:42:11.21,中文,,0,0,0,,是的，他们有名字的话，也会教给我们\N{\r英文}Yes, so that we can learn their names, if they have names,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.28,0:42:13.40,中文,,0,0,0,,然后再介绍代词\N{\r英文}and then introduce pronouns later.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.52,0:42:15.12,中文,,0,0,0,,这些都是小学教的\N{\r英文}These are all grade-school words.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.00,0:42:17.80,中文,,0,0,0,,吃，走\N{\r英文}"Eat." "Walk."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.04,0:42:21.48,中文,,0,0,0,,给我解释下\N{\r英文}Help me understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.44,0:42:23.56,中文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\r英文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.72,0:42:29.48,中文,,0,0,0,,别，别擦，别擦上面的\N{\r英文}No, no, no, not the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.20,0:42:33.80,中文,,0,0,0,,“你们到访地球的目的？”
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.92,0:42:37.20,中文,,0,0,0,,好，这就是你想问的，对吧？\N{\r英文}Okay, this is where you wanna get to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.28,0:42:38.72,中文,,0,0,0,,- 就是这个  - 好\N{\r英文}- That is the question.  - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.80,0:42:42.56,中文,,0,0,0,,那我们首先要确定，他们懂得什么是“问题”\N{\r英文}So, first we need to make sure that they understand what a question is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.68,0:42:47.24,中文,,0,0,0,,本质是我们发起请求\N{\r英文}Okay? The nature of a request for information
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.32,0:42:48.76,中文,,0,0,0,,来获取信息\N{\r英文}along with a response.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.84,0:42:52.08,中文,,0,0,0,,然后我们还得解释清楚\N{\r英文}Then, we need to clarify
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.16,0:42:56.32,中文,,0,0,0,,“你”跟“你们”有什么区别\N{\r英文}the difference between a specific "you" and a collective "you,"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.40,0:43:00.80,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我们并不关心某个外星人被派来做什么\N{\r英文}because we don't want to know why Joe Alien is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.88,0:43:03.36,中文,,0,0,0,,而是想搞清他们共同到访的目的\N{\r英文}We want to know why they all landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.76,0:43:07.08,中文,,0,0,0,,而目的又需要懂得意图\N{\r英文}And "purpose" requires an understanding of intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.16,0:43:09.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得搞清这是他们自觉的选择\N{\r英文}We need to find out, do they make conscious choices
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.00,0:43:12.20,中文,,0,0,0,,亦或是受本能驱使\N{\r英文}or is their motivation so instinctive
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.28,0:43:15.36,中文,,0,0,0,,以至于对提问根本不会有反应\N{\r英文}that they don't understand a "why" question at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.44,0:43:19.57,中文,,0,0,0,,而重中之重，我们得跟他们建立起足够的词汇量\N{\r英文}And... And biggest of all, we need to have enough vocabulary with them
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.64,0:43:21.64,中文,,0,0,0,,能让我们明白他们的回答\N{\r英文}that we understand their answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.76,0:43:25.52,中文,,0,0,0,,懂了\N{\r英文}I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.64,0:43:27.24,中文,,0,0,0,,遵照你的单子\N{\r英文}Stick to your list.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.12,0:43:32.64,中文,,0,0,0,,千万...别乱加词进去\N{\r英文}Just don't add anything to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.88,0:43:51.52,中文,,0,0,0,,重力0.97G，氧气浓度21.4%，完毕\N{\r英文}Gravity, 0.97. Oxygen level, 21.4%. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.60,0:43:53.84,中文,,0,0,0,,秃鹫，A队已就位\N{\r英文}Condor, Alpha's now in the main.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.92,0:43:56.32,中文,,0,0,0,,正布置设备和遥测装置，完毕\N{\r英文}Setting up equipment and telemetry. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.40,0:43:57.73,中文,,0,0,0,,我们开始吧\N{\r英文}Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.08,0:44:09.20,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}"Louise."
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.24,0:44:12.08,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝，我叫路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise. I am Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.16,0:44:20.65,中文,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\N{\r英文}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.72,0:44:24.32,中文,,0,0,0,,那是新符号吗？我分不清\N{\r英文}Is that a new symbol? I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.40,0:44:27.32,中文,,0,0,0,,不是吧，我觉得还是表示“人类”的符号\N{\r英文}I don't know I think it's the symbol for "human" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.40,0:44:31.68,中文,,0,0,0,,只是收尾处略弯了点，或许这表示提问\N{\r英文}It just has a little curl on the end, maybe to indicate a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.76,0:44:32.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我也不敢肯定\N{\r英文}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.36,0:44:34.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我也一样，路易丝\N{\r英文}I don't know, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.36,0:44:37.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得他们没明白\N{\r英文}I think they're getting confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.36,0:44:40.64,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士，我们继续下一个词吧\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks, perhaps we should move on to the next word.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.60,0:45:00.64,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.72,0:45:04.37,中文,,0,0,0,,- 没事的  - 什么情况？\N{\r英文}- It's okay, Nate.  - What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.44,0:45:06.52,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿，嘿，你在做什么？\N{\r英文}Hey, hey, hey. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.64,0:45:08.88,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我没事  - 你疯了吗？\N{\r英文}- Yeah, I'm fine.  - Are you insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.96,0:45:10.20,中文,,0,0,0,,得让他们见到我的真面目\N{\r英文}They need to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.72,0:45:12.48,中文,,0,0,0,,她要脱掉核生化防护服  班克斯博士！\N{\r英文}She's taking off her hazmat suit. Dr. Banks!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.84,0:45:16.04,中文,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？\N{\r英文}Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.12,0:45:17.48,中文,,0,0,0,,你有感染的危险\N{\r英文}You're risking contamination.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.20,0:45:19.48,中文,,0,0,0,,得让他们见到我的真面目\N{\r英文}They need to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.56,0:45:20.56,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.00,0:45:23.00,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.08,0:45:24.12,中文,,0,0,0,,她朝玻璃墙走去了\N{\r英文}She's walking towards the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.28,0:45:28.88,中文,,0,0,0,,要终止任务吗？\N{\r英文}Should we abort?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.96,0:45:31.56,中文,,0,0,0,,请求收到，等候口头指令\N{\r英文}Request noted. Stand by for frag order.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.64,0:45:32.68,中文,,0,0,0,,回到你们的位置\N{\r英文}Go back to your stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.32,0:46:50.64,中文,,0,0,0,,这才算是正式见面\N{\r英文}Now that's a proper introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.72,0:46:51.80,中文,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\r英文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.16,0:47:04.20,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}"Louise."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.44,0:47:09.09,中文,,0,0,0,,我叫路易丝\N{\r英文}I am Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.76,0:47:12.04,中文,,0,0,0,,伊恩，你不介绍自己吗？\N{\r英文}Ian, you want to introduce yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.92,0:47:17.08,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\r英文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.28,0:47:21.44,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.12,0:47:27.16,中文,,0,0,0,,豁出去了\N{\r英文}Screw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.88,0:47:33.45,中文,,0,0,0,,人都有一死，对吧？\N{\r英文}Everybody dies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.24,0:47:38.97,中文,,0,0,0,,长官，唐纳利也脱掉了防护服\N{\r英文}Sir, Donnelly is taking off his hazmat suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.04,0:47:40.48,中文,,0,0,0,,准许终止任务？\N{\r英文}Permission to abort?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.08,0:47:42.52,中文,,0,0,0,,继续对话进程\N{\r英文}Continue the session.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.04,0:48:00.12,中文,,0,0,0,,伊恩\N{\r英文}Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.80,0:48:01.92,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.80,0:48:04.84,中文,,0,0,0,,你呢？\N{\r英文}You.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.64,0:48:07.97,中文,,0,0,0,,你们叫什么？\N{\r英文}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.40,0:48:37.05,中文,,0,0,0,,这应该是他们的名字\N{\r英文}I think those are their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.92,0:48:42.25,中文,,0,0,0,,他们也有名字\N{\r英文}They have names.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.08,0:48:44.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我们该如何称呼他们呢？\N{\r英文}So, what are we gonna call them?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.64,0:48:46.64,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\r英文}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.16,0:48:50.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我推荐阿波特和科斯特洛\N{\r英文}I was thinking Abbott and Costello.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.07,0:48:51.27,中文,,0,0,0,,{\an8}阿波特和科斯特洛是1940到1950年间好莱坞著名的喜剧搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.28,0:48:54.28,中文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\r英文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.68,0:48:56.56,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好吗？  - 好，很好\N{\r英文}- Yeah?  - Yeah, I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.04,0:49:00.24,中文,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\r英文}I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.20,0:49:17.12,中文,,0,0,0,,一队人员，下车后\N{\r英文}Team 1, exit your vehicle
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.20,0:49:20.36,中文,,0,0,0,,直接前往污染物净化室\N{\r英文}and proceed directly ahead to the decontamination tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.20,0:49:30.09,中文,,0,0,0,,在进入设备间前，请别取下你们的面具\N{\r英文}Leave your respirator on until you reach the equipment room.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.88,0:50:00.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\r英文}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.04,0:50:12.44,中文,,0,0,0,,二队人员，下车后直接前往污染物净化室\N{\r英文}Team 2, exit your vehicles and continue to the decontamination tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.80,0:50:15.32,中文,,0,0,0,,在进入设备间前\N{\r英文}Leave your respirators on
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.40,0:50:18.52,中文,,0,0,0,,千万别取下你们的面具\N{\r英文}and do not hesitate until you reach the equipment room.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.08,0:50:23.28,中文,,0,0,0,,你感觉如何？\N{\r英文}How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.36,0:50:25.72,中文,,0,0,0,,疲劳过度\N{\r英文}Overworked.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.44,0:50:29.92,中文,,0,0,0,,不用我多说你也明白，这样做有多危险\N{\r英文}Well, I guess I don't need to tell you, you're putting yourself at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.16,0:50:33.92,中文,,0,0,0,,并没有辐射中毒的迹象\N{\r英文}There are no signs of radiation poisoning yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.00,0:50:35.88,中文,,0,0,0,,等你的血检出来后，我们再确认\N{\r英文}We'll see how your blood tests look.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.52,0:50:38.36,中文,,0,0,0,,目前嘛，我再给你打一针加强剂\N{\r英文}For now, I'm gonna give you another boost.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.44,0:50:39.72,中文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\r英文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.84,0:50:42.36,中文,,0,0,0,,没有辐射中毒\N{\r英文}No radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.44,0:50:44.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我们没查出任何异样\N{\r英文}Nothing else we can detect either,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.12,0:50:46.60,中文,,0,0,0,,不过为了以防外一，我还是给他们打了加强剂\N{\r英文}but I'd give 'em a strong cocktail regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.68,0:50:49.28,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我们头一回取得实质进展\N{\r英文}It's the first time we've made significant progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.12,0:50:52.48,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\r英文}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.00,0:50:54.80,中文,,0,0,0,,我们就冒这一回险\N{\r英文}We'll take the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.44,0:50:57.28,中文,,0,0,0,,- 宝贝  - 那边到底什么情况？\N{\r英文}- Okay, honey...  - What is going on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.36,0:50:59.88,中文,,0,0,0,,- 宝贝  - 你一个字都不能透露？\N{\r英文}- Honey.  - Is there anything you can tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.96,0:51:02.88,中文,,0,0,0,,不能，你不用担心，好吗？\N{\r英文}No... You don't need to worry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.96,0:51:05.36,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我怎么能不担心？  -冷静点\N{\r英文}- How can I not worry?  - Just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.44,0:51:06.52,中文,,0,0,0,,冷静点\N{\r英文}Just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.40,0:51:10.48,中文,,0,0,0,,贝基吵着问我，那些怪物会不会把爹地杀了\N{\r英文}Becky asked me if the monsters are going to kill Daddy,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.56,0:51:12.92,中文,,0,0,0,,宝贝，那是不可能的\N{\r英文}Honey, it's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.84,0:51:17.41,中文,,0,0,0,,一定要注意安全\N{\r英文}Just stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.48,0:51:18.72,中文,,0,0,0,,你不用担心\N{\r英文}You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.80,0:51:20.68,中文,,0,0,0,,请务必，我好害怕\N{\r英文}Please, I'm so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.84,0:51:28.08,中文,,0,0,0,,所有初级外星语言学家和科研人员必须遵守\N{\r英文}All junior xenolinguistics and science personnel must observe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.16,0:51:30.76,中文,,0,0,0,,宵禁命令，除非有指挥官的特别授权\N{\r英文}general curfew unless expressly authorized
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.84,0:51:33.52,中文,,0,0,0,,可以进行加班工作\N{\r英文}for extended work hours by unit COs.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.60,0:51:37.20,中文,,0,0,0,,宵禁每晚10点开始\N{\r英文}Curfew in effect as of 2200 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.76,0:51:41.89,中文,,0,0,0,,通知到所有晚班人员，消防人员，守夜人员\N{\r英文}Notice to all late workers, fire watchers and night staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.96,0:51:46.36,中文,,0,0,0,,即刻生效，宵夜整晚供应\N{\r英文}Effective immediately, midnight rations will be served all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.72,0:52:38.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我们仍然对七肢桶的许多方面一无所知\N{\r英文}Here are some of the many things we don't know about heptapods.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.56,0:52:42.00,中文,,0,0,0,,hepta源自古希腊语，表示七，pod，表示脚\N{\r英文}Greek. Hepta, "Seven. " Pod, "Foot."
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.08,0:52:44.40,中文,,0,0,0,,七只脚，故称七肢桶\N{\r英文}"Seven feet." Heptapod.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.08,0:52:47.44,中文,,0,0,0,,他们是何方神圣？\N{\r英文}Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.84,0:52:51.20,中文,,0,0,0,,试图从任何有意义的角度来回答\N{\r英文}Trying to answer thisin any meaningful way
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.28,0:52:52.96,中文,,0,0,0,,都困难重重\N{\r英文}is hampered by the fact that,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.04,0:52:55.40,中文,,0,0,0,,因为外界既看不到、也听不到他们\N{\r英文}outside being able to see them and hear them,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.48,0:52:58.60,中文,,0,0,0,,七肢桶不留下任何蛛丝马迹\N{\r英文}the heptapods leave absolutely no footprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.48,0:53:03.68,中文,,0,0,0,,他们宇宙飞船的化学组成仍未可知\N{\r英文}The chemical composition of their spaceship is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.76,0:53:07.81,中文,,0,0,0,,“蛋壳”不产生废物，不排出气体，也没有辐射\N{\r英文}The shell emits no waste, no gas, no radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.88,0:53:10.56,中文,,0,0,0,,假设“蛋壳”之间有互有通讯\N{\r英文}Assuming that the shells communicate with each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.64,0:53:12.21,中文,,0,0,0,,那他们手段高明，悄无声息\N{\r英文}they do so without detection.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.84,0:53:17.48,中文,,0,0,0,,“蛋壳”内的空气不会被超声波或光波干扰\N{\r英文}The air between the shells is untroubled by sonic emission or light wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.44,0:53:22.17,中文,,0,0,0,,他们是科学家，还是观光客？\N{\r英文}Are they scientists or tourists?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.24,0:53:25.60,中文,,0,0,0,,他们是科学家的话，为什么提问并不积极\N{\r英文}If they're scientists, they don't seem to ask a lot of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.64,0:53:30.56,中文,,0,0,0,,他们为什么要停在现在的地方？\N{\r英文}Why did they park where they did?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.28,0:53:34.28,中文,,0,0,0,,世界上最富盛名的专家也是一头雾水\N{\r英文}The world's most decorated experts can't crack that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.80,0:53:37.92,中文,,0,0,0,,最受推崇的理论是，他们选择的地点都是\N{\r英文}The most plausible theory is that they chose places on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.00,0:53:39.96,中文,,0,0,0,,地球上闪电出现机率最低的\N{\r英文}with the lowest incidence of lightning strikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.80,0:53:42.64,中文,,0,0,0,,可也有个别例外\N{\r英文}But there are exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.72,0:53:46.24,中文,,0,0,0,,另一种候选理论是，这些地点都跟上世纪80年代\N{\r英文}The next most plausible theory is that Sheena Easton had a hit song
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.40,0:53:48.20,中文,,0,0,0,,{\an8}席娜·伊斯顿：苏格兰著名歌星
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.32,0:53:49.52,中文,,0,0,0,,席娜·伊斯顿的流行歌曲有关  所以... 我们只是瞎猜\N{\r英文}at each of these sites in 1980. So, we just don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.48,0:53:54.44,中文,,0,0,0,,他们之间如何交流？\N{\r英文}How do they communicate?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.00,0:53:57.48,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝的工作成果，令我们自惭形秽\N{\r英文}Here, Louise is putting us all to shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.12,0:54:01.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我们取得的首个突破是发现七肢桶\N{\r英文}The first breakthrough was to discover that there's no correlation
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.84,0:54:05.04,中文,,0,0,0,,的书写和口语之间并无关联\N{\r英文}between what a heptapod says and what a heptapod writes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.03,0:54:14.93,中文,,0,0,0,,伊恩走路
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.12,0:54:25.84,中文,,0,0,0,,不像任何人类文字，他们的书写是会意象形语标文字\N{\r英文}Unlike all written human languages, their writing is semasiographic.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.92,0:54:29.28,中文,,0,0,0,,只传达意思，并无对应的发音\N{\r英文}It conveys meaning. It doesn't represent sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.36,0:54:38.36,中文,,0,0,0,,或许我们的书写，在他们看来是多余的\N{\r英文}Perhaps they view our form of writing as a wasted opportunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.56,0:54:40.80,中文,,0,0,0,,浪费了第二个交流渠道\N{\r英文}passing up a second communications channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.56,0:54:48.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要感谢巴基斯坦的朋友\N{\r英文}We have our friends in Pakistan
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.24,0:54:52.45,中文,,0,0,0,,他们贡献了对七肢桶书写的研究\N{\r英文}to thank for their study of how heptapods write.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.52,0:54:56.73,中文,,0,0,0,,因为和说话不同，语标不受时间限制\N{\r英文}Because, unlike speech, a logogram is free of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.40,0:55:01.84,中文,,0,0,0,,与他们的飞船、身体相似\N{\r英文}Like their ship or their bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.92,0:55:05.12,中文,,0,0,0,,他们的书写文字不存在先后顺序\N{\r英文}their written language has no forward or backward direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.80,0:55:08.96,中文,,0,0,0,,语言学家称之为非线性拼写\N{\r英文}Linguists call this "nonlinear orthography,"
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.04,0:55:12.48,中文,,0,0,0,,这不禁让人疑问：“他们也是这样思考的吗？”\N{\r英文}which raises the question, "Is this how they think?"
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.60,0:55:17.28,中文,,0,0,0,,想象你要用双手写一个句子\N{\r英文}Imagine you wanted to write a sentence using two hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.36,0:55:19.08,中文,,0,0,0,,同时从2头开始\N{\r英文}starting from either side.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.08,0:55:22.76,中文,,0,0,0,,你得想好要写的每一个字\N{\r英文}You would have to know each word you wanted to use
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.88,0:55:25.72,中文,,0,0,0,,以及它们占用的空间\N{\r英文}as well as how much space that it would occupy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.64,0:55:29.76,中文,,0,0,0,,而七肢桶在2秒内就能轻松写出\N{\r英文}A heptapod can write a complex sentence
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.84,0:55:31.96,中文,,0,0,0,,一个复杂的句子\N{\r英文}in two seconds, effortlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.04,0:55:34.77,中文,,0,0,0,,而我们做个最简单的回复，都要花上一个月\N{\r英文}It's taken us a month to make the simplest reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.48,0:55:38.24,中文,,0,0,0,,下一步，扩充词汇量\N{\r英文}Next, expanding vocabulary.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.32,0:55:41.44,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝认为怎么都要花上一个月\N{\r英文}Louise thinks it could easily take another month to be ready for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.28,0:56:00.32,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\r英文}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.84,0:56:02.88,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\r英文}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.96,0:56:04.84,中文,,0,0,0,,韦伯正找你呢\N{\r英文}Weber's looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.76,0:56:08.52,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯，你以为我躲在这干嘛？\N{\r英文}Yeah, well, why do you think I'm hiding out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.00,0:56:11.24,中文,,0,0,0,,上来啊\N{\r英文}Come on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.16,0:56:13.24,中文,,0,0,0,,来\N{\r英文}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.32,0:56:14.40,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\r英文}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.68,0:56:19.12,中文,,0,0,0,,这地方不错吧？\N{\r英文}Nice out here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.04,0:56:21.80,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯，风景不错\N{\r英文}Yeah, it's a nice view.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.68,0:56:24.28,中文,,0,0,0,,远离喧嚣\N{\r英文}Away from the noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.64,0:56:29.76,中文,,0,0,0,,其实，我刚好想到你\N{\r英文}You know, I was just thinking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.44,0:56:34.56,中文,,0,0,0,,你处理语言的方式挺像数学家\N{\r英文}You approach language like a mathematician.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.64,0:56:36.21,中文,,0,0,0,,你自己也知道吧？\N{\r英文}You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.28,0:56:40.36,中文,,0,0,0,,我就当你是恭维我啊\N{\r英文}I will take that as a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.76,0:56:41.84,中文,,0,0,0,,就是恭维\N{\r英文}Yeah, well, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.32,0:56:45.44,中文,,0,0,0,,多亏了你\N{\r英文}It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.64,0:56:48.21,中文,,0,0,0,,我们才能避开那些沟通陷阱\N{\r英文}I watch you steer us around these communication traps
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.28,0:56:50.24,中文,,0,0,0,,不然我还蒙在鼓里\N{\r英文}that I didn't even know existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.32,0:56:51.60,中文,,0,0,0,,说的什么啊\N{\r英文}Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.08,0:56:56.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我单身就是这个原因吧\N{\r英文}I guess that's why I'm single.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.12,0:56:59.28,中文,,0,0,0,,不是打击你，懂得去沟通还不足以\N{\r英文}Trust me, you can understand communication
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.36,0:57:01.08,中文,,0,0,0,,让你脱单啊\N{\r英文}and still end up single.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.36,0:57:13.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我总觉得那里面发生的一切\N{\r英文}I feel like everything that happens in there
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.92,0:57:16.12,中文,,0,0,0,,都和我们俩有关\N{\r英文}comes down to the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.56,0:57:21.20,中文,,0,0,0,,这是好事，对吧？你和我？\N{\r英文}Yeah, it's a good thing though, right? You and I?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.76,0:57:27.68,中文,,0,0,0,,整天和些废物一起工作，你也受不了吧？\N{\r英文}Have you seen the jokers that we're working with?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.56,0:57:30.32,中文,,0,0,0,,能遇到你，真是老天有眼\N{\r英文}I'm glad I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.51,0:57:36.31,中文,,0,0,0,,外星人危机 第25天 委内瑞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.26,0:57:39.23,中文,,0,0,0,,外星人危机 第25天 塞拉利昂
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.33,0:57:41.07,中文,,0,0,0,,伦敦  拯救我们的种族！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.80,0:57:44.92,中文,,0,0,0,,今晚，第一张外星人的照片开始疯传\N{\r英文}Tonight, the first photograph of the aliens goes viral.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.52,0:57:49.28,中文,,0,0,0,,环保组织警告，蒙大拿存在的主要风险因子\N{\r英文}Biological contamination is a major risk factor at the Montana site,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.40,0:57:51.68,中文,,0,0,0,,就是生化污染\N{\r英文}so say environmental pressure groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.76,0:57:53.84,中文,,0,0,0,,在华盛顿，80万市民走上街头\N{\r英文}Eight-hundred thousand march on Washington
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.92,0:57:56.57,中文,,0,0,0,,抗议政府的危机应对\N{\r英文}to protest the government's handling of the crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.64,0:57:59.24,中文,,0,0,0,,别走开，还有更多的特别报道\N{\r英文}All this, and more special coverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.12,0:58:03.48,中文,,0,0,0,,...有人在那东西里和外星人接触\N{\r英文}First contact with whoever it is that is inside that thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.56,0:58:05.44,中文,,0,0,0,,猜猜是谁在导演？当然是政府啊\N{\r英文}and who do we have running the show? The government.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.52,0:58:07.48,中文,,0,0,0,,没错，就是这个政府\N{\r英文}That's right, folks. The same government
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.56,0:58:10.32,中文,,0,0,0,,搞砸了我们的医疗保险，搞垮了我们的军队\N{\r英文}who ruined our healthcare and bankrupted our military.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.40,0:58:11.40,中文,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这些人\N{\r英文}Look at these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.48,0:58:13.36,中文,,0,0,0,,他们大多数人连枪都没有\N{\r英文}Most of them don't even have guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.60,0:58:15.72,中文,,0,0,0,,面对着可能的全面入侵\N{\r英文}We could be facing a full-scale invasion,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.80,0:58:17.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的总统却一味忍让\N{\r英文}and our president is just willing to sit back
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.80,0:58:19.72,中文,,0,0,0,,对他们采取绥靖政策\N{\r英文}and let them waltz in and take our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.80,0:58:22.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我们就要完蛋了，醒醒吧大家！\N{\r英文}We are falling asleep at the wheel, people.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.28,0:58:24.16,中文,,0,0,0,,你们知道我说的是事实，肯定知道\N{\r英文}You know what I'm talking about. I know you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.24,0:58:26.52,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我们应该展现武力,威慑对方\N{\r英文}What if the smartest thing we could do right now
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.60,0:58:28.64,中文,,0,0,0,,这才是上上策吧？\N{\r英文}would be to give them a show of force?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.72,0:58:30.80,中文,,0,0,0,,最好是向他们发出警告\N{\r英文}I'm talking about a shot across the bow
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.88,0:58:31.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我想了解听众朋友的观点\N{\r英文}I wanna hear what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.96,0:58:34.61,中文,,0,0,0,,请拨打热线电话，发表下你对目前局势的看法\N{\r英文}Caller number one, you're on the air. What do you think about all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.28,0:59:02.80,中文,,0,0,0,,这个词怎么念？\N{\r英文}What's this word?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.00,0:59:20.28,中文,,0,0,0,,行星\N{\r英文}"Planet."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.00,0:59:22.28,中文,,0,0,0,,不，不\N{\r英文}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.92,0:59:29.00,中文,,0,0,0,,比方说，地球是颗行星\N{\r英文}That's, like... The Earth is a planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.00,0:59:32.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我在加略特老师课上做的东西，你要看吗？\N{\r英文}Want to see my project from Miss Garriott's class?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.00,0:59:34.33,中文,,0,0,0,,好啊，小肉鼻\N{\r英文}Yeah, little nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.92,0:59:39.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要做自己的电视节目\N{\r英文}We had to make up our own TV show.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.84,0:59:42.17,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们有的话\N{\r英文}If we had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.24,0:59:45.56,中文,,0,0,0,,- 这两个人是谁？  - 你和爸爸\N{\r英文}- And who are those two people?  - That's you and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.56,0:59:49.32,中文,,0,0,0,,节目叫“爸爸妈妈与动物交谈”\N{\r英文}The show is called Mommy and Daddy Talk to Animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.56,0:59:53.21,中文,,0,0,0,,真有爱\N{\r英文}Well, it's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.64,0:59:58.76,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\r英文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.84,1:00:04.92,中文,,0,0,0,,你有权不开心，因为你爸爸和我...\N{\r英文}You know it's okay to be sad that your dad and I...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.00,1:00:06.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我懂，我没事\N{\r英文}I know. I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.84,1:00:10.72,中文,,0,0,0,,我们俩都很爱你\N{\r英文}'Cause we both love you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.80,1:00:13.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我懂，这只是幅卡通，不代表什么\N{\r英文}I know. It's just a cartoon. Not real.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.88,1:00:15.04,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝？\N{\r英文}Louise?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.52,1:00:20.85,中文,,0,0,0,,你还好吗？\N{\r英文}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.00,1:00:23.20,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\r英文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.72,1:00:25.05,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯，没什么\N{\r英文}Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.36,1:00:31.04,中文,,0,0,0,,就是我想给你解释，也可能会力不从心\N{\r英文}I'm not sure it's something I can explain.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.12,1:00:33.52,中文,,0,0,0,,你没去凯文医生那检查下吗？\N{\r英文}When was your last checkup with Dr. Kettler?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.20,1:00:35.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\r英文}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.12,1:00:37.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我出去透透气\N{\r英文}I'm gonna get some air.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.40,1:00:39.56,中文,,0,0,0,,不用担心\N{\r英文}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.64,1:00:41.24,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好吧  - 我没事\N{\r英文}- All right.  - I'm fine. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.52,1:01:42.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你感觉好些了吗？\N{\r英文}How you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.36,1:01:50.64,中文,,0,0,0,,我需要补充睡眠，不过还挺得住\N{\r英文}I need some sleep, but I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.88,1:01:52.96,中文,,0,0,0,,真的？\N{\r英文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.52,1:01:57.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我最近在研读一种理论，里面讲到\N{\r英文}You know, I was doing some reading about this idea that
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.80,1:02:01.12,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你全身心的钻研一门外语\N{\r英文}if you immerse yourself into a foreign language,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.20,1:02:03.93,中文,,0,0,0,,整个人都会骤然改变\N{\r英文}that you can actually rewire your brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.00,1:02:06.44,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯，是萨丕尔-沃夫假说\N{\r英文}Yeah, the Sapir-Whorf Hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.72,1:02:08.96,中文,,0,0,0,,这种理论\N{\r英文}The theory that...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.72,1:02:11.72,中文,,0,0,0,,这种理论认为\N{\r英文}It's the theory that
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.80,1:02:15.40,中文,,0,0,0,,你所讲的语言能决定你的思维模式\N{\r英文}the language you speak determines how you think and...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.48,1:02:18.64,中文,,0,0,0,,对，这能影响到你的世界观\N{\r英文}Yeah. It affects how you see everything. It was...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.56,1:02:21.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我想问下\N{\r英文}I'm curious,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.16,1:02:23.32,中文,,0,0,0,,你做梦都在说他们的语言吗？\N{\r英文}are you dreaming in their language?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.40,1:02:36.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我是做过这样的梦，可我觉得...\N{\r英文}I may have had a few dreams, but I don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.76,1:02:41.36,中文,,0,0,0,,并不会因此而误了工作\N{\r英文}I don't think that that makes me unfit to do this job.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.76,1:03:01.76,中文,,0,0,0,,你有睡觉吗？\N{\r英文}Did you sleep?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.52,1:03:03.64,中文,,0,0,0,,睡了会儿\N{\r英文}A little.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.40,1:03:05.68,中文,,0,0,0,,你懂中文吗?\N{\r英文}Do you know Mandarin?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.00,1:03:11.52,中文,,0,0,0,,变化了\N{\r英文}It is shifting.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.48,1:03:22.56,中文,,0,0,0,,你马上要听的声音是来自中国军队的最高统帅\N{\r英文}The voice you're about to hear belongs to China's military chief,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.40,1:03:25.81,中文,,0,0,0,,尚将军\N{\r英文}General Shang.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.76,1:03:28.12,中文,,0,0,0,,戴上耳机\N{\r英文}Pull it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.04,1:03:33.04,中文,,0,0,0,,这有卫星信号，你可以边看边听\N{\r英文}We got a satellite feed here of who he's talking to,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.20,1:03:34.69,中文,,0,0,0,,确定他说了什么\N{\r英文}if you want to look.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.72,1:03:37.05,中文,,0,0,0,,等等，往回倒\N{\r英文}Wait, go back.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.72,1:03:40.08,中文,,0,0,0,,停\N{\r英文}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.08,1:03:46.00,中文,,0,0,0,,他说这12艘船都会给我们先进技术\N{\r英文}He's saying that each of the 12 is offering advanced technology.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.48,1:03:50.76,中文,,0,0,0,,再回倒，播放\N{\r英文}And back again. And play.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.24,1:03:58.21,中文,,0,0,0,,“我们的科学家团队正尝试破译集合”\N{\r英文}"Our science team is attempting to decode the sets."
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.92,1:04:00.92,中文,,0,0,0,,“集合”，我不明白是什么意思\N{\r英文}"Sets." I don't know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.60,1:04:03.25,中文,,0,0,0,,能获取优势之类的\N{\r英文}Something about advantage.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.40,1:04:05.84,中文,,0,0,0,,“西服，荣誉，花朵”\N{\r英文}"Suits, honor, and flowers."
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.12,1:04:07.36,中文,,0,0,0,,我不...\N{\r英文}I don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.84,1:04:10.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我不明白，就这样\N{\r英文}I don't know, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.68,1:04:12.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我也搞不明白\N{\r英文}I don't know what it means either.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.92,1:04:15.68,中文,,0,0,0,,一小时前，中国的军队开始集结\N{\r英文}An hour ago, China mobilized forces.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.76,1:04:17.64,中文,,0,0,0,,现在俄罗斯也响应了\N{\r英文}And now, Russia is following suit.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.36,1:04:20.12,中文,,0,0,0,,尚打定主意要行动了\N{\r英文}Shang's about to start something.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.60,1:04:22.60,中文,,0,0,0,,跟着西装（跟牌）... 西装...\N{\r英文}Following suit, "suits".
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.76,1:04:27.33,中文,,0,0,0,,是序数牌，字牌，花牌\N{\r英文}Suits. Honor. Flowers.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.40,1:04:30.08,中文,,0,0,0,,上校，这些都是麻将里的牌\N{\r英文}Colonel, those are all tile sets in mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.96,1:04:33.29,中文,,0,0,0,,天啊，难道他们\N{\r英文}God, are they...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.92,1:04:36.92,中文,,0,0,0,,他们在用游戏和七肢桶沟通吗？\N{\r英文}Are they using a game to converse with their heptapods?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.64,1:04:40.32,中文,,0,0,0,,有可能...这又如何？\N{\r英文}Maybe. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.40,1:04:44.20,中文,,0,0,0,,假如我不教英语，而是教七肢桶国际象棋\N{\r英文}Well, let's say that I taught them chess instead of English.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.28,1:04:46.04,中文,,0,0,0,,通过游戏来进行每句对话\N{\r英文}Every conversation would be a game,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.12,1:04:49.44,中文,,0,0,0,,在对弈的过程中传递每个想法，只有胜负之分\N{\r英文}every idea expressed through opposition, victory, defeat.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.52,1:04:50.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你还不明白？\N{\r英文}You see the problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.08,1:04:55.05,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我只给你把锤子\N{\r英文}If all I ever gave you was a hammer...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.16,1:04:56.57,中文,,0,0,0,,你看什么都像钉子\N{\r英文}Everything's a nail.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.60,1:05:00.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我们必须问重大问题\N{\r英文}We need to ask the big question.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.96,1:05:03.16,中文,,0,0,0,,等不了了\N{\r英文}Ready or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.52,1:05:08.56,中文,,0,0,0,,对，所以...\N{\r英文}Right, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.64,1:05:10.60,中文,,0,0,0,,好，告诉我你所使用的温度，好吗？\N{\r英文}Okay, let me know what temperature you use, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.96,1:05:14.53,中文,,0,0,0,,不对，这个和以前一样\N{\r英文}No, this is the same as before.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.12,1:05:16.16,中文,,0,0,0,,- 看  - 我...\N{\r英文}- See.  - I...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.80,1:05:18.32,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯，不，可是在3和4之间\N{\r英文}Yeah, no, but between three and four.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.28,1:05:21.85,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好了，该走了  - 好的\N{\r英文}- All right, time to go.  - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.96,1:05:35.85,中文,,0,0,0,,还有96分钟可以进行对话，完毕\N{\r英文}Ninety-six minutes remaining in the session. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.56,1:05:45.68,中文,,0,0,0,,好\N{\r英文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.88,1:05:50.96,中文,,0,0,0,,“七肢桶 目的”\N{\r英文}Heptapod's purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.64,1:06:05.21,中文,,0,0,0,,“七肢桶 目的 地球” 你们来地球的目的？\N{\r英文}Heptapod purpose. Earth. What is your purpose?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.76,1:06:13.96,中文,,0,0,0,,只有科斯特洛一人？\N{\r英文}Do we only have Costello?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.40,1:06:21.20,中文,,0,0,0,,很好，你出现了\N{\r英文}Okay. There you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.52,1:06:44.76,中文,,0,0,0,,他说了什么？\N{\r英文}What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.60,1:06:55.12,中文,,0,0,0,,给武器\N{\r英文}"Offer weapon."
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.00,1:07:01.20,中文,,0,0,0,,你可是亲眼看到他们写的\N{\r英文}But you saw what they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.28,1:07:02.61,中文,,0,0,0,,用的那个词他们还没完全搞明白\N{\r英文}Using a word they don't fully understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.68,1:07:04.09,中文,,0,0,0,,- 这可能只是个请求  - 或者是警告\N{\r英文}- It could be just a request.  - Or a warning.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.16,1:07:05.20,中文,,0,0,0,,够了\N{\r英文}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.76,1:07:06.76,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.48,1:07:09.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我们并不知道他们\N{\r英文}We don't know if they understand
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.60,1:07:12.08,中文,,0,0,0,,是否分得清武器和工具\N{\r英文}the difference between a weapon and a tool.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.76,1:07:14.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的语言如同文化般繁杂\N{\r英文}Our language, like our culture, is messy,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.80,1:07:16.37,中文,,0,0,0,,有时一个词能表达两种意思\N{\r英文}and sometimes one can be both.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.44,1:07:20.04,中文,,0,0,0,,他们很可能想说的是，让我们给他们东西\N{\r英文}I think it's quite possible that they're asking us to offer them something,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.12,1:07:23.40,中文,,0,0,0,,而不是反过来，就像贸易的雏形\N{\r英文}not the other way around, like the first part of a trade.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.56,1:07:26.80,中文,,0,0,0,,那除了这两个词，我们如何才能搞清他们的意图?\N{\r英文}So, how do we clarify their intentions beyond those two words?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.92,1:07:28.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我再回去\N{\r英文}Well, I go back in.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.32,1:07:30.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我们立刻返回，找出真相\N{\r英文}Right away, we go back in and we clear this up.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.56,1:07:31.64,中文,,0,0,0,,实际操作要比那麻烦得多\N{\r英文}It's more complicated than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.72,1:07:32.88,中文,,0,0,0,,哪麻烦了，你说说看？\N{\r英文}How is it more complicated than that?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.80,1:07:38.12,中文,,0,0,0,,上校，国防部长要跟你通话\N{\r英文}Colonel, the Secretary of Defense is on the line for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.28,1:07:48.68,中文,,0,0,0,,在我们搞清这个之前，一定要保守秘密\N{\r英文}We need to sit on this information till we know what it means.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.76,1:07:50.25,中文,,0,0,0,,不能让我们的敌人知道了\N{\r英文}So, we aren't sharing it with our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.32,1:07:51.65,中文,,0,0,0,,我们还必须考虑一种可能性\N{\r英文}We have to consider the idea
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.72,1:07:53.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的访客想以此来挑拨我们内斗\N{\r英文}that our visitors are prodding us to fight among ourselves
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.96,1:07:56.24,中文,,0,0,0,,直到仅有一方胜出\N{\r英文}until only one faction prevails.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.32,1:07:57.48,中文,,0,0,0,,你这么说根本没有依据\N{\r英文}There's no evidence of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.56,1:07:58.92,中文,,0,0,0,,明显有\N{\r英文}Sure there is.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.00,1:08:00.84,中文,,0,0,0,,随便翻开本史书\N{\r英文}Just grab a history book.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.16,1:08:03.84,中文,,0,0,0,,英国同印度，德国同卢旺达\N{\r英文}The British with India, the Germans with Rwanda.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.92,1:08:07.00,中文,,0,0,0,,在匈牙利他们还专门造了个词\N{\r英文}They even got a name for it in Hungary.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.04,1:08:13.16,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\r英文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.84,1:08:16.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的世界是多极的\N{\r英文}We're a world with no single leader.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.60,1:08:19.08,中文,,0,0,0,,七肢桶不可能只挑选一国来打交道\N{\r英文}It's impossible to deal with just one of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.16,1:08:20.84,中文,,0,0,0,,现在又提到了武器\N{\r英文}And with the word "weapon" now...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.68,1:08:22.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我是哈尔彭\N{\r英文}Halpern.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.04,1:08:25.20,中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\r英文}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.68,1:08:42.52,中文,,0,0,0,,收到，等候指令\N{\r英文}Copy that. Waiting for instructions.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.60,1:08:44.32,中文,,0,0,0,,还没确认\N{\r英文}No confirmation yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.40,1:08:45.84,中文,,0,0,0,,继续等待\N{\r英文}Standing by.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.20,1:08:47.32,中文,,0,0,0,,有消息吗？\N{\r英文}Anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.84,1:08:50.17,中文,,0,0,0,,他们说了什么\N{\r英文}What did they say?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.12,1:08:53.44,中文,,0,0,0,,中国和俄罗斯都离线了，还指望他们能说什么\N{\r英文}China and Russia are off the grid. They aren't speaking to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.72,1:08:56.64,中文,,0,0,0,,不管他们在上一次对话中了解到什么，都被吓到了\N{\r英文}Whatever they learned in their last session has them spooked.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.48,1:09:00.64,中文,,0,0,0,,遵命，长官\N{\r英文}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.12,1:09:02.53,中文,,0,0,0,,命令我们也离线\N{\r英文}We have orders to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.64,1:09:03.80,中文,,0,0,0,,等等，这些可是我们的盟友\N{\r英文}Wait, these are our allies.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.88,1:09:04.96,中文,,0,0,0,,上校，你不能这么做\N{\r英文}Colonel, you can't shut us down.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.04,1:09:06.76,中文,,0,0,0,,- 关掉我们的无线电  - 照办\N{\r英文}- Put us on radio silence.  - Do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.24,1:09:08.48,中文,,0,0,0,,七肢桶给我们的消息是...\N{\r英文}We received a message from the...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.68,1:09:11.04,中文,,0,0,0,,该死！\N{\r英文}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.72,1:09:13.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我们需要保持对话\N{\r英文}We need to be talking to each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.08,1:09:15.60,中文,,0,0,0,,你想跟他们对话？先搞清这是什么意思\N{\r英文}You wanna talk to them? Find out what this means.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.24,1:09:23.04,中文,,0,0,0,,大本营之间的通讯已中断\N{\r英文}Base-camp talk is now offline.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.44,1:09:26.01,中文,,0,0,0,,- 所有的翻译...  - 还没确认，他们都离线了\N{\r英文}- All interpreters... - No confirmation. They're offline.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.08,1:09:29.05,中文,,0,0,0,,...都退下，向部门联络员报道\N{\r英文}...stand down and report to unit coordinators.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.20,1:09:33.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我们之前都没有重启过对话\N{\r英文}We've never re-entered a session before.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.24,1:09:35.92,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝，相信我好吗？我们还来得及\N{\r英文}Look, Louise, trust me, okay? We've got time.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.00,1:09:37.88,中文,,0,0,0,,只需要加快进度，对吧？\N{\r英文}We've just gotta step on it, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.80,1:09:40.13,中文,,0,0,0,,“使用武器”\N{\r英文}"Use weapon."
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.68,1:09:41.84,中文,,0,0,0,,这是外星人发出的信息\N{\r英文}This is the alien message
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.92,1:09:43.84,中文,,0,0,0,,促使中国政府在今天\N{\r英文}said to have provoked the Chinese government
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.92,1:09:47.60,中文,,0,0,0,,下令让他们的科学家退出国际合作任务\N{\r英文}to withdraw their scientists from the international mission today.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.20,1:09:50.52,中文,,0,0,0,,在一份声明中，尚将军说道\N{\r英文}In a statement, General Shang said,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.60,1:09:54.00,中文,,0,0,0,,对外星人的分化图谋，中方表示遗憾\N{\r英文}"China no longer trusts the aliens who want to divide us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.08,1:09:55.57,中文,,0,0,0,,会以保护全人类为己任\N{\r英文}"Humanity must be protected."
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.24,1:09:59.24,中文,,0,0,0,,中国请求联合国召开紧急会议\N{\r英文}China has asked for immediate talks at the UN.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.40,1:10:05.05,中文,,0,0,0,,A19，这是秃鹫，完毕\N{\r英文}Alpha one-niner, this is Condor. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.60,1:10:12.20,中文,,0,0,0,,A19，这是秃鹫\N{\r英文}Alpha one-niner, this is Condor.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.28,1:10:13.80,中文,,0,0,0,,请讲，完毕\N{\r英文}Come in. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.72,1:10:20.32,中文,,0,0,0,,马克斯上尉，这是秃鹫\N{\r英文}Captain Marks, Condor.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.40,1:10:23.56,中文,,0,0,0,,没有收到回复，收到的话，请回答\N{\r英文}Not receiving transmission. Squelch twice if you hear mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.92,1:10:28.16,中文,,0,0,0,,马克斯上尉，护送人员被要求停止一切行动\N{\r英文}Captain Marks, all escort groups are ordered to cease all activity.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.16,1:11:01.24,中文,,0,0,0,,不，不行，班克斯博士，你不能进去\N{\r英文}No, no, no. Dr. Banks, you can't go in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.36,1:11:02.64,中文,,0,0,0,,就让我问一个问题\N{\r英文}We just need to ask one question.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.72,1:11:06.00,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士，这次对话已经结束了，你不能...\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks, the session is finished. You can't...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.28,1:11:07.61,中文,,0,0,0,,你不能再进去，会有危险的\N{\r英文}You can't go back in. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.68,1:11:09.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我们只需要5分钟，别紧张\N{\r英文}Look, we just need five minutes. Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.48,1:11:11.44,中文,,0,0,0,,马克斯，放他们进去\N{\r英文}Marks, let them go.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.36,1:11:16.04,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿，阿波特\N{\r英文}Hey, Abbott.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.24,1:11:24.21,中文,,0,0,0,,那么，我们该如何称呼？第37次对话？\N{\r英文}So, what are we calling this, session 37?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.64,1:11:26.29,中文,,0,0,0,,不，第36次对话第二段\N{\r英文}No, 36, part two.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.40,1:11:27.52,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\r英文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.96,1:11:29.04,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\r英文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.80,1:11:35.88,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么他们单独进去了？\N{\r英文}Why they on their own?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.96,1:11:37.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我一直在试着联系马克斯上尉\N{\r英文}We've been attempting to hail Captain Marks.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.00,1:11:39.80,中文,,0,0,0,,护送小队不肯回应，长官\N{\r英文}The escort units are not responding, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.88,1:11:40.88,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么不回应？\N{\r英文}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.24,1:11:43.57,中文,,0,0,0,,派出安保人员\N{\r英文}Send security.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.84,1:11:50.28,中文,,0,0,0,,给武器，问号\N{\r英文}"Offer weapon. Question mark."
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.24,1:11:57.44,中文,,0,0,0,,你们要给我们什么吗？\N{\r英文}Are you offering us something?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.56,1:12:09.13,中文,,0,0,0,,“技术，设备，方法”？\N{\r英文}"Technology. Apparatus. Method"?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.56,1:12:11.68,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯，瞧见了吗？这是不同的词\N{\r英文}Yeah, see, this is a different word.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.76,1:12:14.24,中文,,0,0,0,,这个弧线，它要臃肿得多\N{\r英文}This segment, it's a lot busier.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.96,1:12:21.08,中文,,0,0,0,,给\N{\r英文}"Give.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.04,1:12:23.45,中文,,0,0,0,,技术\N{\r英文}"Technology.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.00,1:12:26.08,中文,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\r英文}"Now."
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.84,1:12:36.44,中文,,0,0,0,,他在做什么？\N{\r英文}What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.04,1:12:43.61,中文,,0,0,0,,上尉，看你十点钟方向\N{\r英文}Captain, on your 10.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.00,1:12:49.65,中文,,0,0,0,,反叛人员必须立即逮捕\N{\r英文}Mutineers are to be apprehended without engaging.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.76,1:12:52.52,中文,,0,0,0,,不能让他们激怒我们的访客，完毕\N{\r英文}We don't want to risk antagonizing our visitors. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.28,1:12:56.48,中文,,0,0,0,,安保分队接近中，长官  4分钟后到达\N{\r英文}Security detail inbound, sir. T-minus four minutes remaining.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.60,1:12:58.17,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得拿出对策\N{\r英文}We need to see this through.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.36,1:12:59.93,中文,,0,0,0,,好了，武器上膛，做好准备\N{\r英文}Okay, this is it. Lock and load.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.00,1:13:01.92,中文,,0,0,0,,只要拖住他们，就能确保任务完成\N{\r英文}We just need to hold them off until it's done.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.00,1:13:04.52,中文,,0,0,0,,明白 只需警告性射击，压制住他们\N{\r英文}Copy that. Warning shots and suppressive fire only.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.60,1:13:05.84,中文,,0,0,0,,都上膛，找掩护\N{\r英文}Load up and get to cover.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.92,1:13:07.84,中文,,0,0,0,,保持镇定，尽量不要造成伤亡\N{\r英文}Stay fresh and we can avoid casualties.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.96,1:13:37.53,中文,,0,0,0,,阿波特想让我去屏障那写\N{\r英文}Abbott wants me to write on the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.32,1:13:43.84,中文,,0,0,0,,你有这个本事？\N{\r英文}Can you even do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.44,1:13:46.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\r英文}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.16,1:14:04.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我用双手写不了\N{\r英文}I can't do it with both hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.76,1:15:17.76,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.16,1:15:34.16,中文,,0,0,0,,那是什么声音？\N{\r英文}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.24,1:15:36.97,中文,,0,0,0,,- 自由开火  - 快过来，我中枪了，我中枪了\N{\r英文}- Free fire!  - Over there! I'm hit! I'm hit!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.08,1:16:22.68,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿，嘿，别忙着起来\N{\r英文}Hey, hey, hey. Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.76,1:16:24.25,中文,,0,0,0,,你遭受了脑震荡\N{\r英文}You suffered a concussion.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.32,1:16:25.84,中文,,0,0,0,,还是躺着吧\N{\r英文}Just lay back.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.52,1:16:30.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你感觉如何？\N{\r英文}How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.80,1:16:40.16,中文,,0,0,0,,伊恩怎么样了？\N{\r英文}How is Ian?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.28,1:16:42.20,中文,,0,0,0,,和你一样 没什么大碍\N{\r英文}Same as you. He's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.84,1:16:45.00,中文,,0,0,0,,谁...\N{\r英文}Who...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.44,1:16:46.93,中文,,0,0,0,,是谁干的？\N{\r英文}Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.28,1:16:50.04,中文,,0,0,0,,几个小兵 看电视看傻了\N{\r英文}Some soldiers. Been watching too much TV.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.84,1:16:55.28,中文,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\N{\r英文}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.36,1:16:57.44,中文,,0,0,0,,别紧张，别紧张\N{\r英文}Now, take it easy. Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.52,1:16:59.28,中文,,0,0,0,,营地不再安全了\N{\r英文}The site's no longer secure.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.36,1:17:00.93,中文,,0,0,0,,我们正等待疏散\N{\r英文}We're standing by to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.20,1:17:02.48,中文,,0,0,0,,伊恩呢？\N{\r英文}Where's Ian?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.84,1:17:06.65,中文,,0,0,0,,大约10分钟前，韦伯把他叫走了\N{\r英文}Weber came and got him maybe 10 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.72,1:17:09.72,中文,,0,0,0,,得知你没事，他才肯离开的\N{\r英文}But he wouldn't leave until he knew you were okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.20,1:17:13.80,中文,,0,0,0,,帐篷里的人都在连轴转\N{\r英文}The whole tent is on the clock
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.88,1:17:16.61,中文,,0,0,0,,想破解七肢桶给你的那个天书\N{\r英文}to figure out whatever it is you were given up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.84,1:17:24.52,中文,,0,0,0,,全都在这了？\N{\r英文}This is all of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.88,1:17:26.64,中文,,0,0,0,,图像信号没有因爆炸而中断？\N{\r英文}The feed wasn't interrupted by the explosion?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.88,1:17:29.88,中文,,0,0,0,,据我所知是这样\N{\r英文}Not as far as we can see.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.56,1:17:33.16,中文,,0,0,0,,有你能看懂的吗？\N{\r英文}You see something?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.24,1:17:34.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我还不知道\N{\r英文}I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.56,1:17:37.48,中文,,0,0,0,,先得把我和路易丝的团队都召集起来\N{\r英文}I'm gonna need my team to get together with Louise's team.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.56,1:17:38.89,中文,,0,0,0,,这需要大家群策群力\N{\r英文}I need everybody working on this.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.96,1:17:39.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我们还不能离开\N{\r英文}We cannot leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.84,1:17:42.04,中文,,0,0,0,,很高兴你醒了\N{\r英文}Glad to see you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.12,1:17:44.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我们必须回去，我们得向他们解释，这不是我们的过错\N{\r英文}We need to go back in and we need to explain to them this wasn't our fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.96,1:17:47.00,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我们不能再回去了  - 我们必须回去，跟他们解释\N{\r英文}- We can't go back inside.  - We have to tell them... We have to.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.20,1:17:49.16,中文,,0,0,0,,在那里面发生的是一起袭击\N{\r英文}What happened in there was an attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.24,1:17:52.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我们可以指望最好的结果，可也要做好迎接报复的准备\N{\r英文}We can hope for the best, but I have orders to prepare for retaliation.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.24,1:17:53.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我们或许只能疏散\N{\r英文}We may have to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.60,1:17:57.49,中文,,0,0,0,,那样做就错了，只要他们还停在那，我们就应该坚守\N{\r英文}No, that's the wrong move. As long as they stay, we have to stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.28,1:18:33.44,中文,,0,0,0,,他们并没飞走\N{\r英文}Well, they're not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.04,1:18:37.28,中文,,0,0,0,,我怎么觉得要出大事？\N{\r英文}Why does this feel worse?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.84,1:18:43.68,中文,,0,0,0,,中国摆出了进攻架势\N{\r英文}China is on the offensive.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.76,1:18:47.04,中文,,0,0,0,,他们正调动军队，准备对外星人飞船发起攻击\N{\r英文}They're positioning their military to blow the alien vessel right out of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.12,1:18:48.45,中文,,0,0,0,,一旦开战\N{\r英文}And if this happens,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.52,1:18:53.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我们不能坐以待毙，所以开始准备吧\N{\r英文}we can't sit around waiting for retaliation, so get prepared.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.28,1:18:55.32,中文,,0,0,0,,空军和陆军正待命中\N{\r英文}The Air Force and infantry are standing by.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.40,1:18:56.40,中文,,0,0,0,,遵命\N{\r英文}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.32,1:18:58.40,中文,,0,0,0,,突发新闻
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.16,1:19:01.28,中文,,0,0,0,,今晚，中国成为首个向外星人\N{\r英文}Tonight, China becomes the first world power
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.36,1:19:03.60,中文,,0,0,0,,宣战的世界大国\N{\r英文}to declare war against the aliens.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.52,1:19:08.04,中文,,0,0,0,,在联合国的外交斡旋宣告失败后\N{\r英文}Following the failure of diplomatic efforts at the United Nations,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.12,1:19:11.48,中文,,0,0,0,,中国对外证实，他们的语言专家在今晚\N{\r英文}China has confirmed that its language experts have, tonight,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.60,1:19:14.60,中文,,0,0,0,,向上海的外星人下达了最后通牒\N{\r英文}delivered an ultimatum at the Shanghai site.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.68,1:19:16.80,中文,,0,0,0,,在一份电视声明中\N{\r英文}In a televised statement, General Shang,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.88,1:19:19.04,中文,,0,0,0,,中国人民解放军最高统帅，尚将军\N{\r英文}Chairman of the People's Liberation Army,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.12,1:19:22.80,中文,,0,0,0,,限令外星人24小时内撤出中国\N{\r英文}said the aliens have 24 hours to leave Chinese territory
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.88,1:19:24.56,中文,,0,0,0,,不然将遭到毁灭性打击\N{\r英文}or face destruction.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.64,1:19:27.84,中文,,0,0,0,,他还敦促其他国家的领导人与中国联合起来\N{\r英文}And he urged all other world leaders to unite with China
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.92,1:19:30.44,中文,,0,0,0,,采取一致行动\N{\r英文}and take a similar stance.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.52,1:19:33.88,中文,,0,0,0,,巴基斯坦，俄罗斯和苏丹都在本国的着陆点\N{\r英文}With a huge buildup of forces at their landing sites,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.96,1:19:39.04,中文,,0,0,0,,集结起大军 预计会紧随中国采取行动\N{\r英文}Pakistan, Russia, and Sudan are thought to be following China's lead.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.64,1:19:56.60,中文,,0,0,0,,这肯定有章可循\N{\r英文}It can't be random.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.04,1:20:14.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我们怎么也得研究数年\N{\r英文}It's going to take us years.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.20,1:20:21.08,中文,,0,0,0,,这里该用什么术语？\N{\r英文}What's this term here?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.08,1:20:26.41,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\r英文}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.44,1:20:29.52,中文,,0,0,0,,老妈？\N{\r英文}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.04,1:20:32.16,中文,,0,0,0,,宝贝怎么了？\N{\r英文}Sweetie?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.24,1:20:34.68,中文,,0,0,0,,用来形容那个的术语\N{\r英文}What's this term for that thing like a...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.76,1:20:35.96,中文,,0,0,0,,像是科技术语\N{\r英文}Like a technical term?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.76,1:20:40.04,中文,,0,0,0,,就是我们达成协议，双方都有收获那种？\N{\r英文}Where we make a deal and we both get something out of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.12,1:20:41.69,中文,,0,0,0,,妥协吗？\N{\r英文}"Compromise."
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.76,1:20:42.88,中文,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\r英文}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.56,1:20:48.44,中文,,0,0,0,,就好比竞争一样，但结果令双方都满意\N{\r英文}Like, it's a competition, but both sides end up happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.92,1:20:51.20,中文,,0,0,0,,是双赢吗？\N{\r英文}Like a win-win.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.92,1:20:53.44,中文,,0,0,0,,还要更有科学性\N{\r英文}More science-y than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.20,1:20:56.48,中文,,0,0,0,,你要问科学方面的，去打给你父亲\N{\r英文}If you want science, call your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.12,1:21:12.45,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\r英文}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.12,1:21:24.48,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\r英文}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.88,1:21:27.28,中文,,0,0,0,,没事的，我醒了\N{\r英文}It's okay. I'm up.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.28,1:21:33.88,中文,,0,0,0,,现在什么时候了？\N{\r英文}What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.16,1:21:38.28,中文,,0,0,0,,是你该拿出上等香槟庆祝的时候了\N{\r英文}It's time you open that bottle you've been hiding.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.84,1:21:44.16,中文,,0,0,0,,你有突破了，是吧？\N{\r英文}You cracked something, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.24,1:21:45.44,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯，快过来\N{\r英文}Yeah, come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.60,1:21:49.01,中文,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这部分\N{\r英文}Take a look at this section.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.48,1:21:51.52,中文,,0,0,0,,好像跟时间有关\N{\r英文}It seems to be talking about time.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.60,1:21:55.00,中文,,0,0,0,,他们表示“时间”的符号无处不在\N{\r英文}Their symbol for "time" is everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.08,1:21:56.73,中文,,0,0,0,,这到底说的什么？\N{\r英文}So, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.68,1:22:00.72,中文,,0,0,0,,超光速旅行的方案吗？\N{\r英文}A formula for faster-than-light travel?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.80,1:22:02.16,中文,,0,0,0,,谁敢下结论？\N{\r英文}Who can tell?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.08,1:22:04.57,中文,,0,0,0,,里面有大段空白\N{\r英文}There are too many gaps.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.64,1:22:05.84,中文,,0,0,0,,全都不完整\N{\r英文}Nothing's complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.16,1:22:07.60,中文,,0,0,0,,然后我恍然大悟\N{\r英文}Then it dawned on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.68,1:22:09.01,中文,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\r英文}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.84,1:22:12.00,中文,,0,0,0,,就这儿\N{\r英文}Right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.32,1:22:16.24,中文,,0,0,0,,别盯着有字的区域，注意空白区域\N{\r英文}Stop focusing on the ones, look at the zeroes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.32,1:22:19.52,中文,,0,0,0,,整个空间里面，有数据的区域和空白区域各占了多少？\N{\r英文}How much of this is data? How much of it is negative space?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.96,1:22:22.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我于是测了下\N{\r英文}So, I measured it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.52,1:22:26.20,中文,,0,0,0,,数据的比例是0.0833...\N{\r英文}0.0833 recurring.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.84,1:22:35.12,中文,,0,0,0,,或许你想用分数来表达\N{\r英文}Perhaps you'd like that as a fraction.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.36,1:22:40.20,中文,,0,0,0,,十二分之一\N{\r英文}One of 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.32,1:22:46.29,中文,,0,0,0,,这里传达出的意思是，这只是十二块之一\N{\r英文}What they're saying right here is that this is one of 12.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.68,1:22:48.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得到的只是全图的一块\N{\r英文}We are part of a larger whole.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.64,1:22:50.40,中文,,0,0,0,,这也有可能是让我们十二方厮杀的诱饵\N{\r英文}Or we're one of 12 contestants for the prize.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.48,1:22:51.64,中文,,0,0,0,,我们为什么要向他汇报？\N{\r英文}Why do I have to talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.72,1:22:53.37,中文,,0,0,0,,我们都是在这为国效命\N{\r英文}We're all working together here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.44,1:22:55.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得联络其他着陆点\N{\r英文}We need to talk to the other sites.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.24,1:22:57.81,中文,,0,0,0,,我们应该主动支援，帮他们理解从其他七肢桶那得到的信息\N{\r英文}We need to help them with what they've gotten from the other heptapods.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.88,1:22:59.60,中文,,0,0,0,,你可别忘了，我们现在通讯管制了\N{\r英文}In case you don't remember, we're blacked out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.80,1:23:02.61,中文,,0,0,0,,中国才威胁说要摧毁他们那的飞船，我们只能靠自己了\N{\r英文}China just threatened to destroy their shell. We're on our own.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.68,1:23:04.48,中文,,0,0,0,,可这给的提示是所有分块能组合起来\N{\r英文}Yeah, but this says that all of the pieces fit together.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.56,1:23:07.00,中文,,0,0,0,,现在根本没人关心这些\N{\r英文}And I'm telling you that no one else cares.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.44,1:23:10.48,中文,,0,0,0,,两小时前，我们从俄国的一个加密频道截取到一段音频\N{\r英文}Two hours ago, we pulled this audio off a secure channel in Russia.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.56,1:23:13.53,中文,,0,0,0,,他们科学团队里的一名成员对外直播的\N{\r英文}Someone on the science team there was broadcasting wide.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.76,1:23:20.16,中文,,0,0,0,,在他们的最后一次对话中，外星人是这样说的：“时候到了...\N{\r英文}In their final session, the alien said, "There is no time.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.24,1:23:22.48,中文,,0,0,0,,”许多合而为一“\N{\r英文}"Many become one."
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.60,1:23:24.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们把武器都给完了\N{\r英文}I feel we have all been given weapons.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.96,1:23:28.08,中文,,0,0,0,,如果有人收到这个的话，请..\N{\r英文}If anyone is receiving this, please...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.48,1:23:36.52,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得...\N{\r英文}Well, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.72,1:23:39.61,中文,,0,0,0,,他刚刚说的话可以有各种解读\N{\r英文}there are a lot of ways you can interpret what he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.68,1:23:41.68,中文,,0,0,0,,不需要翻译来解读我也知道它的意思\N{\r英文}I don't need an interpreter to know what this means.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.76,1:23:43.76,中文,,0,0,0,,俄国为了保密，刚刚处决了\N{\r英文}Russia just executed one of their own experts
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.84,1:23:45.17,中文,,0,0,0,,自己的一名专家\N{\r英文}to keep their secrets.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.32,1:23:47.76,中文,,0,0,0,,“许多合而为一”可能只是他们想表达\N{\r英文}"Many become one" could just be their way of saying,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.96,1:23:49.53,中文,,0,0,0,,“要进行一些组合”的意思\N{\r英文}"Some assembly required."
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.60,1:23:51.60,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么要分成块给我们？\N{\r英文}Why hand it out to us in pieces?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.68,1:23:53.20,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么不给我们完整的？\N{\r英文}Why not just give it all over?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.28,1:23:55.52,中文,,0,0,0,,让我们人类破天荒的合作一次，没有比这更好的办法了吧？\N{\r英文}Well, what better way to force us to work together for once?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.04,1:23:57.64,中文,,0,0,0,,就算我相信你\N{\r英文}Even if I did believe you,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.76,1:24:00.24,中文,,0,0,0,,你有天大的本事吗，能让其他国家乖乖配合\N{\r英文}how in the world you gonna get anybody else to play along
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.32,1:24:01.73,中文,,0,0,0,,交出他们的数据？\N{\r英文}or give up their data?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.88,1:24:04.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我们提供自己的来作交换\N{\r英文}We offer ours in return.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.56,1:24:06.60,中文,,0,0,0,,对\N{\r英文}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.68,1:24:08.20,中文,,0,0,0,,做交易吗？\N{\r英文}What, trade?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.28,1:24:09.64,中文,,0,0,0,,这是非零和博弈\N{\r英文}It's a non-zero sum game.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.44,1:24:13.80,中文,,0,0,0,,非零和博弈\N{\r英文}"Non-zero sum game."
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.96,1:24:17.20,中文,,0,0,0,,就是它\N{\r英文}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.32,1:24:19.04,中文,,0,0,0,,太好了，谢谢\N{\r英文}Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.24,1:24:29.88,中文,,0,0,0,,有9个着陆点都实行了彻底的通讯管制\N{\r英文}Nine of the landing sites have gone total comms blackout.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.00,1:24:32.48,中文,,0,0,0,,要想联络他们，就只有开车去边境\N{\r英文}Only way to reach them is to physically drive there and yell
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.56,1:24:35.21,中文,,0,0,0,,让他们的边防人员传话，我们已经在办了，可这样肯定来不及\N{\r英文}at the border guards, which we're doing, but it won't be fast enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.28,1:24:37.80,中文,,0,0,0,,一定有别的渠道来给他们发消息\N{\r英文}There's got to be a way to... To get the message to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.88,1:24:40.80,中文,,0,0,0,,对我们的盟友可能有，不过到了这种局面，效果有限，也太迟了\N{\r英文}To our allies maybe, but at this stage, it's too little too late.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.88,1:24:43.72,中文,,0,0,0,,世界大战一触即发，我们却还\N{\r英文}What we need is to get all the other nations online
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.80,1:24:45.52,中文,,0,0,0,,联络不上各方，当务之急\N{\r英文}before one starts global war,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.64,1:24:47.68,中文,,0,0,0,,是让有关各国都恢复联网\N{\r英文}and there's no way for us to reach them.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.76,1:24:49.25,中文,,0,0,0,,等下，先等会儿\N{\r英文}Wait. Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.32,1:24:50.56,中文,,0,0,0,,有渠道\N{\r英文}There is.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.44,1:24:53.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我们上方不就有吗\N{\r英文}It's right above us.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.88,1:24:55.60,中文,,0,0,0,,可我们现在很难办到啊\N{\r英文}That's problematic for us right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.12,1:24:58.93,中文,,0,0,0,,五角大楼确信我们这的“蛋壳”会实施报复\N{\r英文}The Pentagon's convinced our shell will retaliate.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.00,1:25:02.20,中文,,0,0,0,,估计一个小时内就要下令疏散了\N{\r英文}My guess is they'll order us to evacuate within the hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.52,1:25:04.01,中文,,0,0,0,,听我说，他们不是敌人\N{\r英文}Look, they're not our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.08,1:25:05.80,中文,,0,0,0,,他们从未有过任何挑衅我们的行为\N{\r英文}They've made no act of aggression towards us.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.88,1:25:07.84,中文,,0,0,0,,或许那就是他们的挑衅方式\N{\r英文}Maybe this is their way of being aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.92,1:25:09.84,中文,,0,0,0,,那不是问题所在\N{\r英文}That's not the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.92,1:25:12.00,中文,,0,0,0,,那问题是什么？\N{\r英文}Well, what is the question?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.48,1:25:15.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我们如何能将你俩送回离地800米高的房间？\N{\r英文}How do we get you back in that room when it's half a mile straight up?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.68,1:25:17.25,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得任务都结束了\N{\r英文}I think our work here is done.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.16,1:25:20.68,中文,,0,0,0,,现在交由我们的上级决断了\N{\r英文}It's in the hands of our superiors now.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.04,1:25:43.08,中文,,0,0,0,,她又想搞什么名堂？\N{\r英文}What the hell is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.20,1:26:39.88,中文,,0,0,0,,不，天啊，天啊\N{\r英文}No. God. Oh, God. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.76,1:29:01.00,中文,,0,0,0,,科斯特洛？\N{\r英文}Costello?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.00,1:29:05.57,中文,,0,0,0,,阿波特呢？\N{\r英文}Where's Abbott?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.49,1:29:18.62,中文,,0,0,0,,“阿波特成了死的了”
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.12,1:29:36.53,中文,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\r英文}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.20,1:29:40.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我们都很抱歉\N{\r英文}We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.88,1:29:46.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我需要你......\N{\r英文}I need you to...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.84,1:29:51.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我需要你发消息给其它着陆点\N{\r英文}I need you to send a message to the other sites.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.57,1:30:00.89,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝有武器
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.86,1:30:10.52,中文,,0,0,0,,使用武器
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.64,1:30:11.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我不\N{\r英文}I don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.48,1:30:14.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\r英文}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.64,1:30:17.76,中文,,0,0,0,,你们来这的目的是什么？\N{\r英文}What is your purpose here?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.70,1:30:27.90,中文,,0,0,0,,我们来帮助人类
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.34,1:30:36.25,中文,,0,0,0,,3000年后......
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.79,1:30:42.26,中文,,0,0,0,,我们需要人类的帮助
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.84,1:30:47.00,中文,,0,0,0,,你怎么能预知未来？\N{\r英文}How can you know the future?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.88,1:31:05.21,中文,,0,0,0,,我不...\N{\r英文}I don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.68,1:31:08.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\r英文}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.00,1:31:11.16,中文,,0,0,0,,这个孩子是谁？\N{\r英文}Who is this child?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.00,1:31:19.32,中文,,0,0,0,,这个节目叫“爸爸妈妈与动物交谈”\N{\r英文}The show is called Mommy and Daddy Talk to Animals.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.77,1:31:34.85,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝能预知未来
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.57,1:31:48.31,中文,,0,0,0,,武器能打开时光隧道
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.76,1:31:54.92,中文,,0,0,0,,等下...\N{\r英文}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.04,1:31:57.08,中文,,0,0,0,,别走，等下！\N{\r英文}No... Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.20,1:32:47.80,中文,,0,0,0,,- 班克斯博士！  - 路易丝！\N{\r英文}- Dr. Banks!  - Louise!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.88,1:32:49.56,中文,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？\N{\r英文}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.92,1:32:54.40,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧？  - 嗯\N{\r英文}- Hey. You all right?  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.48,1:32:56.16,中文,,0,0,0,,过来吧，发生了什么？  - 我没事\N{\r英文}- Here, come on. What happened?  - I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.24,1:32:58.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我正想搞明白，这事关重大\N{\r英文}Tried to figure it out. This is too big.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.08,1:33:00.89,中文,,0,0,0,,现在都不重要了，我们接到命令要疏散了\N{\r英文}Doesn't matter now. We have orders to evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.96,1:33:04.76,中文,,0,0,0,,- 为什么？  - 俄国和苏丹会效仿中国\N{\r英文}- Why?  - Russia and Sudan are following China.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.16,1:33:08.32,中文,,0,0,0,,伊恩，我不明白这是为什么\N{\r英文}Ian. I don't understand why the...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.40,1:33:09.64,中文,,0,0,0,,帮帮我，妈妈\N{\r英文}Help me, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.84,1:33:12.08,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.16,1:33:13.40,中文,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\r英文}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.48,1:33:14.84,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈！\N{\r英文}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.76,1:33:19.20,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈!\N{\r英文}Mama!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.32,1:33:22.76,中文,,0,0,0,,抱歉，宝贝\N{\r英文}Sorry, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.28,1:33:28.60,中文,,0,0,0,,今天星期几，宝贝你知道吗？\N{\r英文}What day is it? Do you know, baby?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.68,1:33:29.92,中文,,0,0,0,,星期天\N{\r英文}Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.60,1:33:38.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你要像爸爸那样离开我吗？\N{\r英文}Are you gonna leave me like Daddy did?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.56,1:33:42.48,中文,,0,0,0,,汉娜宝贝，你爸爸没有离开你\N{\r英文}Hannah, honey, your daddy didn't leave you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.56,1:33:45.04,中文,,0,0,0,,你会见到他的，就这个周末\N{\r英文}You're gonna see him this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.92,1:33:48.60,中文,,0,0,0,,他看我的眼神和以前不同了\N{\r英文}He doesn't look at me the same way anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.04,1:33:58.72,中文,,0,0,0,,这要怪我\N{\r英文}That's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.00,1:34:03.89,中文,,0,0,0,,我跟他说了些事，他一时半会儿没法接受\N{\r英文}I told him something that he wasn't ready to hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.04,1:34:07.24,中文,,0,0,0,,什么事？\N{\r英文}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.52,1:34:13.80,中文,,0,0,0,,信不信由你\N{\r英文}Well, believe it or not,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.88,1:34:16.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道将来会发生的事\N{\r英文}I know something that's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.72,1:34:21.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我也没法解释清楚，我就是知道\N{\r英文}I can't explain how I know. I just do.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.92,1:34:25.92,中文,,0,0,0,,在我告诉你爸爸后，他气坏了\N{\r英文}And when I told your daddy, he got really mad.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.92,1:34:30.68,中文,,0,0,0,,他说我做了错误的选择\N{\r英文}And he said I made the wrong choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.08,1:34:35.44,中文,,0,0,0,,将来会发生什么？\N{\r英文}What? What's going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.72,1:34:42.28,中文,,0,0,0,,会发生的事和一种罕见的疾病有关\N{\r英文}It has to do with a really rare disease.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.60,1:34:47.44,中文,,0,0,0,,并且这种病是势不可挡的\N{\r英文}And it's unstoppable.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.76,1:34:51.60,中文,,0,0,0,,有点像你一样\N{\r英文}Kind of like you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.20,1:34:55.56,中文,,0,0,0,,你是如此神奇，你的诗歌\N{\r英文}Your swimming, and your poetry,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.64,1:34:58.92,中文,,0,0,0,,还有你给世界增添的各种美好事物\N{\r英文}and all the other amazing things that you share with the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.44,1:35:01.32,中文,,0,0,0,,我势不可挡？\N{\r英文}I am unstoppable?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.16,1:35:03.44,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\r英文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.28,1:35:21.64,中文,,0,0,0,,我扶着你\N{\r英文}I got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.48,1:35:24.92,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.64,1:35:27.08,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.44,1:35:31.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我刚得知丈夫为何离开我\N{\r英文}I just realized why my husband left me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.16,1:35:32.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我丈夫离开了我\N{\r英文}My husband left me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.76,1:35:34.56,中文,,0,0,0,,你已经结婚了？\N{\r英文}You were married?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.64,1:35:36.88,中文,,0,0,0,,我们赶紧走吧\N{\r英文}Come on. Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.64,1:36:12.76,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈？\N{\r英文}Mama?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.84,1:36:14.00,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯？\N{\r英文}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.52,1:36:16.64,中文,,0,0,0,,我的名字为什么叫“汉娜”\N{\r英文}Why is my name Hannah?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.40,1:36:18.81,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯，就在这里\N{\r英文}Yeah, got it right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.88,1:36:20.72,中文,,0,0,0,,把这些人送出去\N{\r英文}Get those people back, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.68,1:36:26.81,中文,,0,0,0,,你的名字很特别，因为它是回文\N{\r英文}Well, your name is very special because it is a palindrome.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.88,1:36:30.16,中文,,0,0,0,,顺读倒读均相同的字\N{\r英文}It reads the same forward and backward.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.56,1:36:33.08,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好了，大伙来帮帮我  - 好的，长官\N{\r英文}- All right, guys, give me a hand here.  - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.84,1:36:36.16,中文,,0,0,0,,把它放到那里\N{\r英文}That goes in the back.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.80,1:36:52.37,中文,,0,0,0,,平民承包商准备好授权证章和口令\N{\r英文}Civilian contractors must have their authorization badges
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.44,1:36:53.93,中文,,0,0,0,,以备检查\N{\r英文}and passkeys when checking...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.42,1:36:57.51,中文,,0,0,0,,宇宙文
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.12,1:37:03.56,中文,,0,0,0,,疏散进行中...\N{\r英文}Evacuation underway...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.22,1:37:07.22,中文,,0,0,0,,赠与汉娜
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.04,1:37:08.16,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿！\N{\r英文}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.84,1:37:10.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我们得走了\N{\r英文}Look, we're done here.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.04,1:37:12.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我们把它带走就是了\N{\r英文}We're taking this with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.52,1:37:19.49,中文,,0,0,0,,宇宙文 — 著者：路易丝
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.49,1:37:21.03,中文,,0,0,0,,七文翻译指南
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.32,1:37:38.81,中文,,0,0,0,,我看得懂\N{\r英文}I can read it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.96,1:37:44.76,中文,,0,0,0,,- 我知道它的意思  - 你说什么?\N{\r英文}- I know what it is.  - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.84,1:37:46.92,中文,,0,0,0,,这不是什么武器，这是件礼物\N{\r英文}It's not a weapon, it's a gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.72,1:37:49.48,中文,,0,0,0,,武器是指他们的语言\N{\r英文}The weapon is their language.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.56,1:37:51.60,中文,,0,0,0,,他们全都交给了我们，你明不明白？\N{\r英文}They gave it all to us. Do you understand what that means?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.04,1:37:54.72,中文,,0,0,0,,让我们学他们的语言？先保命再说吧\N{\r英文}So we can learn Heptapod, if we survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.80,1:37:57.69,中文,,0,0,0,,你去学习的话，并且当你真正精通后\N{\r英文}If you learn it, when you really learn it,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.76,1:37:59.92,中文,,0,0,0,,你就会用他们的方式感知时间\N{\r英文}you begin to perceive time the way that they do.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.24,1:38:02.89,中文,,0,0,0,,这样你就能知道将来会发生什么\N{\r英文}So you can see what's to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.96,1:38:05.12,中文,,0,0,0,,而且，他们所理解的时间和我们并不相同\N{\r英文}But time, it isn't the same for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.48,1:38:07.48,中文,,0,0,0,,- 是非线性的  - 听着\N{\r英文}- It's non-linear.  - Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.80,1:38:10.08,中文,,0,0,0,,我们竭尽所能了，可还是差一点\N{\r英文}We did our best, but it wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.40,1:38:13.00,中文,,0,0,0,,你们跟这位上尉走\N{\r英文}The captain will load you up.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.08,1:38:14.52,中文,,0,0,0,,5分钟后起飞\N{\r英文}You're lifting off in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.04,1:38:18.64,中文,,0,0,0,,伊恩，路易丝，跟你们共事是我的荣幸\N{\r英文}Ian, Louise, it was an honor to work with ya.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.72,1:38:21.16,中文,,0,0,0,,一路顺风\N{\r英文}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.48,1:38:25.84,中文,,0,0,0,,上校\N{\r英文}Hey, Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.96,1:38:34.53,中文,,0,0,0,,我去问下我们的目的地\N{\r英文}I'm gonna find out where we're going.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.64,1:38:45.04,中文,,0,0,0,,醒醒，妈妈\N{\r英文}Wake up, Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.48,1:39:22.05,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.24,1:39:24.60,中文,,0,0,0,,很荣幸\N{\r英文}A pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.20,1:39:26.32,中文,,0,0,0,,尚将军\N{\r英文}General Shang.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.40,1:39:27.97,中文,,0,0,0,,是我很荣幸才对\N{\r英文}The pleasure is mine, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.92,1:39:30.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你们的总统说\N{\r英文}Your President said
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.04,1:39:34.32,中文,,0,0,0,,能邀请我参加这个宴会是很荣幸的事\N{\r英文}he was honored to host me at the celebration...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.40,1:39:36.40,中文,,0,0,0,,- 是啊  - 可我要坦白\N{\r英文}- Yes.  - ...but I confess,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.24,1:39:39.89,中文,,0,0,0,,我出席的唯一原因是\N{\r英文}the only reason why I'm here is to
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.40,1:39:43.36,中文,,0,0,0,,想亲自见你一面\N{\r英文}meet you in person.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.36,1:39:46.68,中文,,0,0,0,,我？真是受宠若惊，谢谢你\N{\r英文}Me? Well, I'm flattered. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.76,1:39:50.12,中文,,0,0,0,,18个月前\N{\r英文}Now, 18 months ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.20,1:39:52.24,中文,,0,0,0,,你做了件了不起的事\N{\r英文}you did something remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.92,1:39:56.36,中文,,0,0,0,,连我上司都没这个本事\N{\r英文}Something not even my superior has done.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.24,1:39:59.84,中文,,0,0,0,,是什么事？\N{\r英文}And what's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.92,1:40:01.84,中文,,0,0,0,,你改变了我的心意\N{\r英文}You changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.04,1:40:07.72,中文,,0,0,0,,你是我们能联合起来的原因\N{\r英文}You're the reason for this unification.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.60,1:40:12.40,中文,,0,0,0,,全靠你拨通了我的私人号码\N{\r英文}All because you reached out to me on my private number.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.48,1:40:15.48,中文,,0,0,0,,你的私人号码\N{\r英文}Your private number.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.56,1:40:18.08,中文,,0,0,0,,将军，我并不知道啊\N{\r英文}General, I don't know your private number.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.44,1:40:27.12,中文,,0,0,0,,现在你知道了\N{\r英文}Now you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.32,1:40:31.76,中文,,0,0,0,,我不是想说能看穿你的心思\N{\r英文}I do not claim to know how your mind works,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.44,1:40:37.04,中文,,0,0,0,,不过我相信这号码你一定得看一眼\N{\r英文}but I believe it was important for you to see that.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.48,1:40:40.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我的确打了你的电话，对吧？\N{\r英文}I called you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.44,1:40:43.64,中文,,0,0,0,,是的，你打了\N{\r英文}Yes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.84,1:40:55.96,中文,,0,0,0,,路易丝\N{\r英文}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.52,1:41:15.00,中文,,0,0,0,,好了，都关机吧  - 长官\N{\r英文}- All right, let's shut down the system.  - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.36,1:41:18.76,中文,,0,0,0,,这里有部卫星电话正打给中国\N{\r英文}There's a sat-line here dialing China.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.12,1:41:22.48,中文,,0,0,0,,这里？你什么意思？\N{\r英文}Here? What do you mean "here"?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.00,1:41:26.44,中文,,0,0,0,,快接啊\N{\r英文}Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.76,1:41:29.28,中文,,0,0,0,,那是谁的电话？\N{\r英文}Whose phone is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.44,1:41:34.60,中文,,0,0,0,,是你的电话，长官\N{\r英文}It's your phone, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.28,1:41:43.56,中文,,0,0,0,,搜索营地，马上去办\N{\r英文}Search base camp now.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.00,1:41:45.84,中文,,0,0,0,,给我找出用电话的人\N{\r英文}Find out who's using that phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.44,1:41:48.84,中文,,0,0,0,,- 盯着它的位置  - 遵命\N{\r英文}- Hold on to those coordinates.  - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.92,1:41:51.44,中文,,0,0,0,,快接，我该说什么？\N{\r英文}Come on. What'd I say?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.36,1:41:55.48,中文,,0,0,0,,我该说什么？快接\N{\r英文}What'd I say? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.72,1:42:06.05,中文,,0,0,0,,快接\N{\r英文}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.24,1:42:09.97,中文,,0,0,0,,你跟我说的话，我会永生难忘\N{\r英文}I will never forget what you said.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.60,1:42:23.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你跟我说了我妻子的临终遗言\N{\r英文}You told me my wife's dying words.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.97,1:42:25.77,中文,,0,0,0,,将军
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.27,1:42:30.97,中文,,0,0,0,,我在美国营地
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.57,1:42:33.97,中文,,0,0,0,,将军，你夫人给我托梦了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.37,1:42:38.07,中文,,0,0,0,,妻子的遗愿，你应凭借勇气来......
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.27,1:42:39.17,中文,,0,0,0,,她说你应凭借......
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.36,1:42:42.85,中文,,0,0,0,,我们找到电话源头了\N{\r英文}Found the source of the phone call.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.92,1:42:44.88,中文,,0,0,0,,就在清理间，等候指示\N{\r英文}It's in the clean room. Waiting for instructions.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.96,1:42:47.16,中文,,0,0,0,,应凭借勇气来帮助拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.64,1:42:49.52,中文,,0,0,0,,你在做什么？\N{\r英文}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.20,1:42:52.04,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你在做什么？  - 让一个人改变心意\N{\r英文}- What are you doing?  - Changing someone's mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.12,1:42:54.04,中文,,0,0,0,,- 能帮我争取20秒钟吗？  - 我们来不及了\N{\r英文}- Can you buy me 20 seconds?  - We don't have time for this right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.12,1:42:56.16,中文,,0,0,0,,来得及，相信我，帮我争取20秒，你相信我吗？\N{\r英文}No, trust me, buy me 20 seconds. Do you trust me?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.24,1:42:57.68,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好吧  - 你相信我吗？\N{\r英文}- Okay! Yeah.  - You trust me?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.08,1:42:59.48,中文,,0,0,0,,将军，她还说
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.00,1:43:02.08,中文,,0,0,0,,班克斯博士\N{\r英文}Dr. Banks!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.92,1:43:04.57,中文,,0,0,0,,马上放下电话，不然我们要开枪了\N{\r英文}Drop the phone now or we shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.64,1:43:06.44,中文,,0,0,0,,战争，不成就英雄
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.84,1:43:10.28,中文,,0,0,0,,- 放下！  - 我很抱歉\N{\r英文}- Drop it!  - Yeah. I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.37,1:43:12.37,中文,,0,0,0,,（战争）只会留下孤儿寡母
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.76,1:43:14.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你现在的行为是叛国！\N{\r英文}You're committing an act of treason!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.36,1:43:21.77,中文,,0,0,0,,- 是的  - 放下\N{\r英文}- Yes.  - Drop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.96,1:43:23.45,中文,,0,0,0,,打完了，我打完了\N{\r英文}It's done. I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.22,1:43:31.22,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.32,1:43:34.22,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.92,1:43:43.05,中文,,0,0,0,,12个着陆点的通讯管制今晚仍在持续\N{\r英文}Communications blackout from all 12 landing sites continues this evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.12,1:43:45.84,中文,,0,0,0,,等下，我们刚收到消息\N{\r英文}Hold on, we are just hearing...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.92,1:43:46.92,中文,,0,0,0,,我接到通知\N{\r英文}And I'm being told
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.00,1:43:49.68,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我们要中断这则报道，插播突发新闻\N{\r英文}we're going to cut this report to tell you breaking news.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.76,1:43:52.44,中文,,0,0,0,,突发新闻 中国突然召开了一场新闻发布会\N{\r英文}Breaking now, China has called an emergency press conference.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.52,1:43:55.72,中文,,0,0,0,,中国人民解放军总司令，尚将军\N{\r英文}General Shang, Commander-in-chief of the People's Liberation Army,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.80,1:43:58.04,中文,,0,0,0,,在新闻发布会上宣布\N{\r英文}has announced in an emergency press conference
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.12,1:43:59.80,中文,,0,0,0,,中国会立即撤军\N{\r英文}that China is standing down.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.92,1:44:02.89,中文,,0,0,0,,中国宣布，他们收集到的所有情报\N{\r英文}China is stating that all intelligence they have received
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.96,1:44:05.44,中文,,0,0,0,,将会立即和其他着陆点分享\N{\r英文}will be shared immediately with all the other landing sites.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.52,1:44:08.00,中文,,0,0,0,,世界各地的科学家正认真审查来自英国、日本\N{\r英文}Scientists from around the world are sifting through information received
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.08,1:44:09.41,中文,,0,0,0,,- 等国的信息  - 突发新闻\N{\r英文}- from the UK, Japan...  - Breaking news,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.48,1:44:11.76,中文,,0,0,0,,俄罗斯军队现在公开了他们从自己\N{\r英文}the Russian armed forces are now revealing the information
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.84,1:44:14.08,中文,,0,0,0,,两个着落点收集到的信息\N{\r英文}they've acquired from both of their landing sites
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.16,1:44:16.24,中文,,0,0,0,,并宣布黑海为非军事区\N{\r英文}and have declared the Black Sea a demilitarized zone.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.32,1:44:18.84,中文,,0,0,0,,谜题的十二个分块正被慢慢的拼到一起\N{\r英文}...one of the 12 pieces of this puzzle that's being slowly put together.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.36,1:46:11.04,中文,,0,0,0,,所以，汉娜\N{\r英文}So, Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.24,1:46:14.92,中文,,0,0,0,,这就是你故事的源头\N{\r英文}This is where your story begins.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.08,1:46:18.96,中文,,0,0,0,,他们离去的那天\N{\r英文}The day they departed.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.04,1:46:24.53,中文,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？\N{\r英文}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.76,1:46:31.97,中文,,0,0,0,,尽管已提前知晓人生以及它的走向\N{\r英文}Despite knowing the journey and where it leads,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.32,1:46:37.00,中文,,0,0,0,,我无所畏惧\N{\r英文}I embrace it,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.44,1:46:42.84,中文,,0,0,0,,并且会珍惜每一分钟\N{\r英文}and I welcome every moment of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.48,1:47:02.00,中文,,0,0,0,,H-A-N 汉， N-A-H 娜\N{\r英文}- H-A-N-N-A-H.  - H-A-N-N-A-H.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.80,1:47:21.12,中文,,0,0,0,,现在反过来念  H-A-N 汉， N-A-H 娜\N{\r英文}- Now backward. H-A-N-N-A-H.  - A-N-N-A-H.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.20,1:47:22.69,中文,,0,0,0,,汉娜\N{\r英文}Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.76,1:47:24.33,中文,,0,0,0,,你准备好了，宝贝？\N{\r英文}You ready, baby?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.56,1:47:26.56,中文,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\r英文}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.52,1:47:28.52,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\r英文}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.88,1:47:33.28,中文,,0,0,0,,- 好了吗？  - 好了，你去吧\N{\r英文}- You good?  - All right. See ya.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.04,1:47:36.37,中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\r英文}Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.68,1:47:46.80,中文,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？\N{\r英文}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.88,1:47:48.29,中文,,0,0,0,,让爸爸从你身上翻过去\N{\r英文}Daddy's gonna roll over you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.20,1:47:52.96,中文,,0,0,0,,你准备好了？\N{\r英文}All right, you ready?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.32,1:47:58.65,中文,,0,0,0,,今天讲星星的故事哦\N{\r英文}Guess what? Star stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.56,1:48:03.56,中文,,0,0,0,,- 嗯  - 嗯\N{\r英文}- Yeah.  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.40,1:48:07.64,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你能一览自己的人生，从出生到死亡\N{\r英文}If you could see your whole life from the start to finish,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.92,1:48:12.20,中文,,0,0,0,,你会尝试改变吗？\N{\r英文}would you change things?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.08,1:48:21.84,中文,,0,0,0,,我或许...会尽量多吐露心声\N{\r英文}Maybe I'd say what I feel more often.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.92,1:48:23.36,中文,,0,0,0,,天晓得呢\N{\r英文}I... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.08,1:48:43.56,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道吗，从我能记事起，我就总是对天上的星星着迷\N{\r英文}You know, I've had my head tilted up to the stars for as long as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.04,1:48:48.24,中文,,0,0,0,,可你知道什么让我最惊喜吗？\N{\r英文}You know what surprised me the most?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.40,1:48:52.40,中文,,0,0,0,,并不是遇见他们\N{\r英文}It wasn't meeting them.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.20,1:48:58.88,中文,,0,0,0,,而是遇见你\N{\r英文}It was meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.48,1:49:42.80,中文,,0,0,0,,被你抱着的感觉还是如此温暖啊\N{\r英文}I forgot how good it felt to be held by you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.28,1:49:54.12,中文,,0,0,0,,你想生个宝宝吗？\N{\r英文}You wanna make a baby?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.68,1:50:29.88,中文,,0,0,0,,想\N{\r英文}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.28,1:50:31.28,中文,,0,0,0,,想啊\N{\r英文}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.67,1:50:49.37,中文,,0,0,0,,{\b1}降临{\b}
